WEBVTT

00:48.216 --> 00:53.587
[ Man ]
WE GOT CENIZO,
AND THAT'S PURPLE SAGE.

00:53.654 --> 00:55.556
AGAVE, NOPAL.

00:57.925 --> 00:59.960
WHAT'S THAT STUFF ?

01:00.027 --> 01:03.831
YEAH, THAT'S THAT,
UH, WHATCHAMACALLIT--

01:03.897 --> 01:07.735
THAT'S THAT
HORSE CRIPPLER.

01:09.737 --> 01:13.006
THIS PLACE
IS A GOLD MINE !

01:13.073 --> 01:16.043
LEAD MINE !
WHAT ?

01:16.110 --> 01:18.879
I SAID IT'S
A LEAD MINE !
RIGHT.

01:18.946 --> 01:22.350
I DON'T KNOW WHY
I'M TALKIN' TO YOU.
YOU GOT THAT THING ON YOUR HEAD.

01:22.416 --> 01:24.318
YOU FINDIN' LOTS
OF CACTUS AND SHIT ?

01:24.385 --> 01:27.988
NOT JUST CACTUS.
THERE'S THE ACACIAS,
THE YUCCAS--

01:28.055 --> 01:30.624
LOOKS LIKE A LOT
OF CACTUS TO ME.

01:30.691 --> 01:35.429
MAN KNOWS 150 VARIETIES OF BEER,
CAN'T TELL A POINSETTIA
FROM A PRICKLY PEAR.

01:36.630 --> 01:37.965
HEY, CLIFF !

01:38.031 --> 01:41.068
YOU LIVE IN A PLACE,
YOU SHOULD LEARN
SOMETHIN' ABOUT IT.

01:41.135 --> 01:43.671
EXPLORE !
CLIFF, YOU GOTTA
LOOK AT THIS.

01:45.739 --> 01:49.076
DON'T TELL ME.
SPANISH TREASURE, RIGHT ?

01:49.143 --> 01:53.147
PIECES OF EIGHT FROM
THE CORONADO EXPEDITION ?

01:59.086 --> 02:00.554
JESUS.

02:17.004 --> 02:20.040
WAS CORONADO IN THE MASONS ?

02:20.107 --> 02:23.244
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

02:48.402 --> 02:51.539
* [ Continues ]

03:13.794 --> 03:16.730
* [ Continues ]

03:23.671 --> 03:25.273
* [ Ends ]

03:26.940 --> 03:30.978
[ Man ]
I GOT THE FORENSICS FELLOW
COMIN' DOWN FROM SAN MARCOS.

03:31.044 --> 03:35.416
THERE'S NO WAY TO KNOW
HOW OLD THE BODY IS
WITHOUT SOME LAB WORK.

03:35.483 --> 03:40.454
THAT RING ?
MASONS BEEN AROUND
A LONG WHILE.

03:41.689 --> 03:46.026
IS HE
A TREASURE HUNTER ?
OLD BULLETS.

03:46.093 --> 03:48.929
MAKES ART OUT OF 'EM.

03:50.731 --> 03:53.801
SHERIFF SAYS WE SHOULDN'T
TOUCH ANYTHING, MIKEY.

03:53.867 --> 03:58.506
CAN'T HEAR
WITH THAT RAY GUN. MIKEY !

03:58.572 --> 04:00.341
HEY, WHAT DO WE GOT HERE ?

04:05.513 --> 04:08.616
WE'RE SUPPOSED
TO LEAVE EVERYTHING
RIGHT WHERE WE FOUND IT.

04:08.682 --> 04:11.619
THEY'RE REAL PARTICULAR
ABOUT THAT.

04:12.886 --> 04:15.022
THE SCENE OF THE CRIME.

04:17.591 --> 04:19.927
NO TELLIN' YET
IF THERE'S BEEN A CRIME.

04:22.463 --> 04:26.334
BUT THIS COUNTRY'S SEEN
A GOOD NUMBER OF DISAGREEMENTS
OVER THE YEARS.

04:36.844 --> 04:39.079
[ Woman ]
HE WENT TO SCHOOL ON THE POST
WHEN WE WERE IN KOREA.

04:39.146 --> 04:43.784
IT'S ALL KIDS IN
THE SAME BOAT. ARMY BRATS.
I REALLY NEED--

04:43.851 --> 04:45.953
HIS RECORD SHOWS
THAT HE'S A GOOD STUDENT.

04:46.019 --> 04:50.658
I'M MORE WORRIED
ABOUT THE SOCIAL THING.
ARE THERE GANGS OR GUNS ?

04:50.724 --> 04:54.127
WE HAVEN'T HAD
ANY SERIOUS VIOLENCE,
IF THAT'S WHAT YOU MEAN.

04:54.194 --> 04:59.132
WE'VE GOT A PRETTY
LIVELY MIX, THOUGH: MEXICAN
KIDS, ANGLO KIDS, BLACK KIDS.

04:59.199 --> 05:02.302
AND THE BLACKS ARE--
THEY'RE OUR SMALLEST GROUP.

05:02.370 --> 05:04.938
EXCEPT FOR A COUPLE
OF KICKAPOO KIDS.

05:05.005 --> 05:08.141
LOOK, YOU'RE OBVIOUSLY
A CONCERNED PARENT.

05:08.208 --> 05:11.311
CHET HAS NO HISTORY
OF GETTIN' INTO TROUBLE.

05:11.379 --> 05:15.282
PILAR. IS AMADO OKAY ?

05:15.349 --> 05:18.251
- HE'S NOT HERE ?
- NO. IS HE SICK ?

05:18.318 --> 05:21.722
HE'S GONNA WISH
HE WAS DEAD.

05:21.789 --> 05:24.725
* [ Salsa ]

05:37.270 --> 05:40.408
* [ Continues ]

05:42.610 --> 05:44.612
SOMEBODY HAND ME
THE CD PLAYER.

05:44.678 --> 05:47.448
DAMELO, PENDEJOS.

05:47.515 --> 05:50.851
THEY SURE COME
A LONG WAY SINCE THOSE
OLD 8-TRACK JOBS, AIN'T THEY ?

05:50.918 --> 05:53.286
- SOMETHING WRONG ?
- THIS IS STOLEN PROPERTY.

05:53.353 --> 05:56.056
I'M HAULING
THE BUNCH OF YA TO JAIL.

05:56.123 --> 05:59.092
IF ANYTHING ELSE
IS WRONG, TELL ME ABOUT IT
ON THE WAY TO THE STATION.

05:59.159 --> 06:01.895
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

06:01.962 --> 06:05.232
[ Man ]
...CLEANIN' THE DIRT OUT OF
HIS TOENAILS WITH A POCKETKNIFE.

06:05.298 --> 06:08.001
HE WAS THE MOST HYGIENIC
OF ALL THE McHENRYS.

06:08.068 --> 06:09.637
[ Men Chuckling ]

06:09.703 --> 06:12.740
"FISHBAIT," BUDDY SAYS
IN THAT QUIET WAY OF HIS,

06:12.806 --> 06:16.744
"WHAT DO YOU KNOW
ABOUT THEM TIRES THAT WENT
MISSIN' FROM MERKEL'S ?"

06:16.810 --> 06:18.746
FISHBAIT THINKS
FOR A MINUTE,

06:18.812 --> 06:21.949
THEN LIFTS UP A LOOSE BOARD
FROM THE PORCH FLOOR.

06:22.015 --> 06:27.555
CALLS DOWN INTO IT,
"COME ON OUT, HOOTER !
THEY CAUGHT US !"

06:27.621 --> 06:31.825
[ Laughing ]
BUDDY DEEDS.
HE HAD A WAY.

06:31.892 --> 06:35.295
HE KNOWN WHO IT WAS ON ACCOUNT
OF THE TIRE TRACKS IN THE DIRT,

06:35.362 --> 06:38.532
LEADIN' FROM THE BACK OF THE
GARAGE TO WHERE THEY LOADED UP.

06:38.599 --> 06:41.902
"OLD FISHBAIT," HE SAID,
"NEVER LIFTED A THING
IN THIS WORLD...

06:41.969 --> 06:45.739
IF THERE'S A WAY
HE COULD ROLL IT."

06:45.806 --> 06:47.875
THERE'LL NEVER BE
ANOTHER ONE LIKE HIM.

06:47.941 --> 06:53.481
THAT BOY OF HIS CAN'T CUT IT.
IF YOU ASK ME, HE'S ALL HAT
AND NO CATTLE.

06:53.547 --> 06:55.983
HEY, FELLAS.

06:56.049 --> 06:59.987
SAM ! I WAS JUST TELLIN'
A FEW ON YOUR OLD MAN.

07:00.053 --> 07:03.323
YEAH, HE WAS
A UNIQUE INDIVIDUAL.

07:03.390 --> 07:05.392
HE WAS THAT.

07:05.459 --> 07:10.230
BIG DAY COMIN' UP.
I WISH WE'D HAVE THOUGHT OF IT
WHILE HE WAS STILL LIVIN'.

07:10.297 --> 07:14.502
- WENT SO UNEXPECTED.
- BETTER LATE THAN NEVER.

07:14.568 --> 07:18.572
KOREAN WAR HERO.
SHERIFF FOR NEARLY 30 YEARS.

07:18.639 --> 07:21.041
THE BUDDY DEEDS
MEMORIAL COURTHOUSE.

07:21.108 --> 07:24.645
I HEARD THERE WAS
A BIT OF A FUSS.

07:24.712 --> 07:26.814
WELL, THE USUAL
TROUBLEMAKERS.

07:26.880 --> 07:30.450
DANNY PADILLA WITH THE SENTINEL,
THAT CROWD.

07:30.518 --> 07:34.588
THEY CALL EVERYTHING ELSE
IN THE COUNTRY AFTER
MARTIN LUTHER KING.

07:34.655 --> 07:37.758
WE CAN'T HAVE
ONE MEASLY COURTHOUSE ?

07:37.825 --> 07:39.392
KING WASN'T MEXICAN,
FENTON.

07:39.459 --> 07:42.262
[ Fenton ]
BAD ENOUGH ALL THE STREET NAMES
ARE IN SPANISH.

07:42.329 --> 07:44.231
THEY WERE HERE FIRST.

07:44.297 --> 07:47.034
THEN LET'S CALL IT AFTER
BIG CHIEF SHITINTHEBUCKET.

07:47.100 --> 07:50.303
THAT TONKAWA HAD
THE MEXES BEAT BY CENTURIES.

07:50.370 --> 07:54.241
NINETEEN OUT OF TWENTY PEOPLE
IN THIS TOWN ARE MEXICAN.

07:54.307 --> 07:58.111
THERE WAS A FACTION
PULLIN' FOR THAT BOY KILLED
IN THE GULF WAR. REUBEN--

07:58.178 --> 07:59.813
SANTIAGO.

07:59.880 --> 08:04.351
MEXICANS THAT KNOW,
THAT REMEMBER, UNDERSTAND
WHAT BUDDY WAS FOR THEIR PEOPLE.

08:04.417 --> 08:07.888
HELL, IT WAS MERCEDES OVER THERE
SWUNG THE DECIDING VOTE FOR 'IM.

08:07.955 --> 08:11.124
[ Slamming ]
SHE MADE IT
EVEN THREE TO THREE.

08:11.191 --> 08:14.061
AS MAYOR, I GET
TO CAST THE TIEBREAKER.

08:14.127 --> 08:16.196
THE OLD-TIMERS WON'T
HAVE ANY PROBLEM WITH IT.

08:16.263 --> 08:18.799
THEY REMEMBER HOW BUDDY
COME TO BE SHERIFF.

08:18.866 --> 08:20.834
TELL THAT STORY,
HOLLIS.

08:20.901 --> 08:23.170
HELL, EVERYBODY HEARD
THAT STORY A MILLION TIMES.

08:23.236 --> 08:26.840
I'D LIKE TO HEAR IT.
YOUR VERSION OF IT.

08:26.907 --> 08:29.042
YEAH, COME ON, HOLLIS.

08:32.078 --> 08:35.948
WELL, THE TWO OF US WERE
THE ONLY DEPUTIES BACK THEN.

08:36.015 --> 08:39.152
ME AND BUDDY--
WHAT ? '58 ?

08:39.219 --> 08:40.888
'57, I THINK.

08:40.953 --> 08:45.626
THE SHERIFF AT THE TIME
WAS BIG CHARLIE WADE.

08:45.693 --> 08:51.599
CHARLIE WAS ONE OF YOUR
OLD-FASHIONED, BRIBE-OR-BULLETS
KIND OF SHERIFFS.

08:51.665 --> 08:55.402
HE TOOK A HEALTHY BITE
OUT OF WHATEVER MOVED
THROUGH THIS COUNTY.

08:55.468 --> 09:00.608
IT WAS IN HERE ONE NIGHT,
BACK WHEN JIMMY HERRERA
RUN THE PLACE.

09:00.674 --> 09:03.644
IT STARTED OVER
A BASKET OF TORTILLAS.

09:03.711 --> 09:06.847
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

09:10.851 --> 09:14.822
THIS BEANER FARE
DOESN'T AGREE WITH ME,
BUT THE PRICE SURE IS RIGHT.

09:16.824 --> 09:20.994
JIMMY GOT A KITCHEN
FULL OF WETBACKS,
MOST OF THEM RELATIVES.

09:21.061 --> 09:24.031
THEM PEOPLE
BREED LIKE CHICKENS.

09:26.166 --> 09:28.001
SO ?

09:28.068 --> 09:31.004
SO I ROUST
SOME MUCHACHO ON THE STREET,
DOESN'T HAVE HIS PAPERS.

09:31.071 --> 09:35.508
ALL HE'S GOT TO SAY IS,
YO TRABAJO PARAJIMMY HERRERA.

09:35.575 --> 09:39.813
SORT OF A I-SCRATCH-HIS-BACK,
HE-WASHES-MINE ARRANGEMENT,

09:39.880 --> 09:43.283
IF YOU KNOW WHAT I MEAN.

09:43.350 --> 09:48.555
THIS WILL BE ONE OF
YOUR PICKUPS, BUDDY, FIRST OF
THE MONTH, JUST LIKE THE RENT.

09:48.622 --> 09:50.691
GET THE CAR, HOLLIS.

09:57.297 --> 09:59.032
I'M NOT DOIN' IT.

09:59.099 --> 10:01.802
* [ Continues ]

10:04.738 --> 10:06.840
COME AGAIN ?

10:06.907 --> 10:09.609
IT'S YOUR DEAL.

10:09.677 --> 10:12.312
THERE'S GONNA
BE SOME LEFT OVER FOR YOU.

10:12.379 --> 10:16.349
- I TAKE CARE OF MY BOYS.
- THAT'S NOT THE POINT, CHARLIE.

10:16.416 --> 10:18.652
YOU FEELIN' BAD ABOUT JIMMY ?

10:18.719 --> 10:21.889
HAVE HIM TELL YOU
THE SIZE OF THE MORDIDA
THEY TOOK OUT OF HIS HIDE...

10:21.955 --> 10:24.725
WHEN HE RUN A PLACE
ON THE OTHER SIDE.

10:24.792 --> 10:26.927
THOSE OLD BOYS
FROM CIUDAD LEON--

10:26.994 --> 10:30.397
I'M NOT PICKIN' IT UP.

10:30.463 --> 10:35.402
YOU DO WHATEVER
I SAY YOU DO OR ELSE
YOU PUT IT ON THE TRAIL, SON.

10:41.308 --> 10:44.544
WELL, HOW ABOUT THIS,
CHARLIE ?

10:44.611 --> 10:49.249
HOW ABOUT YOU LAY THAT SHIELD
ON THIS TABLE... AND VANISH...

10:49.316 --> 10:53.086
BEFORE YOU END UP DEAD
OR IN JAIL ?

10:53.153 --> 10:56.056
* [ Continues ]

10:57.090 --> 10:59.392
YOU'RE NOT
MAKIN' SENSE, BUDDY.

10:59.459 --> 11:02.395
YOU STICK AROUND AND
I'M BRINGIN' UP CHARGES
ON THE COUNTY ROAD PROJECT.

11:02.462 --> 11:05.966
TWO-THIRDS OF THAT MONEY
WENT STRAIGHT INTO YOUR POCKET.

11:09.136 --> 11:12.405
YOU'RE BEIN' MIGHTY CARELESS
WITH YOUR MOUTH, SON.

11:18.411 --> 11:22.015
YOU EVER SHOOT A MAN
WHO WAS LOOKIN' YOU
IN THE EYE, CHARLIE ?

11:32.225 --> 11:34.627
IT'S A WHOLE DIFFERENT
STORY, ISN'T IT ?

11:34.694 --> 11:37.030
YOU'RE FIRED.

11:37.097 --> 11:42.502
NOT A SOUL IN THIS COUNTY
ISN'T SICK TO DEATH OF YOUR
BULLSHIT, CHARLIE WADE.

11:42.569 --> 11:45.806
YOU MADE YOURSELF SCARCE,
YOU COULD MAKE
A LOT OF PEOPLE HAPPY.

11:45.873 --> 11:49.442
- YOU LITTLE PISSANT--
- NOW OR LATER,

11:49.509 --> 11:52.746
YOU WON'T HAVE
ANY TROUBLE FINDIN' ME.

11:56.283 --> 11:58.418
YOU'RE A DEAD MAN.

12:03.957 --> 12:08.261
GET THE GODDAMN CAR.
WE'RE GOIN' TO RODERICK'S.

12:19.706 --> 12:21.441
[ Door Slamming ]

12:21.508 --> 12:26.113
MUCHACHO,
MAS CERVEZA, POR FAVOR.

12:26.179 --> 12:28.949
[ Hollis ]
"MAS CERVEZA, POR FAVOR."

12:29.016 --> 12:32.119
[ Fenton ]
THAT BUDDY WAS A COOL BREEZE.

12:32.185 --> 12:36.156
CHARLIE WADE
WERE KNOWN TO PUT QUITE
A FEW PEOPLE IN THE GROUND.

12:36.223 --> 12:40.093
AND YOUR DADDY GETS
EYEBALL TO EYEBALL WITH HIM.

12:40.160 --> 12:43.330
[ Hollis ]
WE MADE OUR PICKUP
AT RODERICK'S PLACE.

12:43.396 --> 12:46.733
NOBODY SEEN HIDE NOR HAIR
OF HIM SINCE.

12:46.800 --> 12:53.273
HE WENT MISSIN' THE NEXT DAY,
ALONG WITH $10,000 IN COUNTY
FUNDS FROM THE SAFE AT THE JAIL.

12:53.340 --> 12:55.242
NEVER HEARD
FROM HIM AGAIN.

12:55.308 --> 12:58.711
[ Fenton ]
BUDDY DEEDS SAID A THING,
HE DAMN WELL BACKED IT UP.

12:58.778 --> 13:02.315
NEVER BE ANOTHER ONE
LIKE HIM.

13:02.382 --> 13:05.886
SO I SUPPOSE THEN HE ARRESTED
ALL OF JIMMY HERRERA'S PEOPLE...

13:05.953 --> 13:09.156
AND SENT 'EM BACK
TO THE OTHER SIDE ?

13:10.924 --> 13:14.061
NO, HE COME TO
AN ACCOMMODATION.

13:14.127 --> 13:19.566
MONEY DOESN'T ALWAYS
HAVE TO CHANGE HANDS
TO KEEP THE WHEELS TURNIN'.

13:19.632 --> 13:22.302
I KNOW YOU HAD PROBLEMS
WITH YOUR FATHER.

13:22.369 --> 13:25.572
AND HE AND MURIEL--
[ Fenton ]
YOUR MOTHER WAS A SAINT.

13:27.440 --> 13:31.144
[ Sighs ]
BUT BUDDY DEEDS
WAS MY SALVATION.

13:32.645 --> 13:34.181
WON'T BE ANOTHER LIKE HIM.

13:36.116 --> 13:39.486
IT IS AN HONOR FOR ME
TO ASSUME COMMAND
OF THIS UNIT.

13:39.552 --> 13:42.255
I'M LOOKING FORWARD
TO WORKING WITH ALL OF YOU.

13:42.322 --> 13:47.060
I'M SURE YOU'RE ALL AWARE
OF THE ARMY'S DECISION
TO SHUT THIS POST DOWN.

13:47.127 --> 13:52.599
THAT DOES NOT MEAN, HOWEVER,
THAT WE ARE HERE TO MARK TIME
UNTIL WE'RE REASSIGNED.

13:52.665 --> 13:58.205
YOU MAY HAVE HEARD RUMORS THAT
I RUN A VERY TIGHT OPERATION.

13:58.271 --> 14:02.609
THESE RUMORS
ARE NOT EXAGGERATED.

14:28.335 --> 14:31.471
* [ Rhythm And Blues ]

14:36.543 --> 14:39.479
[ People Chattering ]

14:48.255 --> 14:51.391
* [ Intensified ]
[ Indistinct ]

14:54.094 --> 14:56.229
WAIT A MINUTE.

14:59.599 --> 15:02.535
[ Woman Laughing ]

15:27.060 --> 15:30.197
* [ Continues ]

15:51.985 --> 15:54.054
[ Popping Sounds ]

15:59.359 --> 16:01.394
GET DOWN !
SOMEBODY
CALL THE DOCTOR !

16:04.197 --> 16:07.067
SOMEBODY CALL THE DOCTOR !

16:07.134 --> 16:09.769
HOLD HIM DOWN !
HOLD HIM DOWN !

16:09.836 --> 16:12.272
SOMEBODY CALL, PLEASE !

16:12.339 --> 16:15.442
YOU WEREN'T IN HERE
TONIGHT, WERE YOU ?
N-NO, SIR.

16:15.508 --> 16:19.546
GO OUT THE BACK WAY.
[ Woman Screaming ]
SOMEBODY CALL THE DOCTOR !

16:20.780 --> 16:23.583
SOMEBODY CALL THE DOCTOR !

16:23.650 --> 16:27.120
JUST TEARIN' EVERYTHING DOWN.
TEARIN' DOWN OUR HERITAGE.

16:27.187 --> 16:30.357
TEARIN' DOWN THE MEMORY
OF PEOPLE WHO FOUGHT
AND DIED FOR THIS LAND.

16:30.423 --> 16:33.060
WE FOUGHT AND DIED
FOR THIS LAND TOO.

16:33.126 --> 16:35.262
WE FOUGHT THE U.S. ARMY,
THE TEXAS RANGERS.

16:35.328 --> 16:39.532
YEAH, AND YOU LOST, BUDDY.
WINNERS GET THE BRAGGIN' RIGHTS.
THAT'S THE WAY IT GOES.

16:39.599 --> 16:44.937
PEOPLE, PEOPLE, IT WOULD BE BEST
IF WE DON'T VIEW THIS THING
IN TERMS OF WINNERS AND LOSERS.

16:45.004 --> 16:47.607
THE WAY SHE'S TEACHIN' IT,
IT'S GOT EVERYTHING
SWITCHED AROUND.

16:47.674 --> 16:50.810
I WAS ON THE TEXTBOOK COMMITTEE,
AND HER VERSION IS NOT--

16:50.877 --> 16:54.447
WE THINK OF THE TEXTBOOK
AS A GUIDE, NOT AS AN ABSOLUTE.

16:54.514 --> 16:57.784
IT IS NOT WHAT
WE SET AS THE STANDARD.

16:57.850 --> 17:01.354
[ Sighs ]
NOW YOU PEOPLE CAN
BELIEVE WHATEVER YOU WANT.

17:01.421 --> 17:03.590
BUT WHEN IT COMES
TO TEACHING OUR CHILDREN--

17:03.656 --> 17:07.660
THEY'RE OUR CHILDREN TOO.
AS A MAJORITY IN THIS COMMUNITY,
WE HAVE THE RIGHT--

17:07.727 --> 17:10.396
THE MEN THAT FOUNDED
THIS STATE HAVE THE RIGHT
TO HAVE THEIR STORY...

17:10.463 --> 17:12.865
TOLD THE WAY IT HAPPENED,
NOT THE WAY SOMEBODY WANTED IT
TO HAPPEN.

17:12.932 --> 17:17.069
THE MEN WHO FOUNDED THIS STATE
BROKE FROM MEXICO BECAUSE THEY
NEEDED SLAVERY TO BE LEGAL...

17:17.137 --> 17:19.239
TO MAKE A FORTUNE
IN THE COTTON BUSINESS.

17:19.306 --> 17:23.410
-THAT'S AN OVERSIMPLIFICATION.
-YOU REPORTIN' THIS MEETING,
DANNY, OR RUNNIN' IT ?

17:23.476 --> 17:25.345
JUST ADDING A LITTLE
HISTORICAL PERSPECTIVE.

17:25.412 --> 17:27.814
YOU CALL IT HISTORY,
I CALL IT PROPAGANDA.

17:27.880 --> 17:31.118
THEY GOT THEIR OWN ACCOUNT
OF THE ALAMO ON THE OTHER SIDE,
BUT WE'RE NOT ON THE OTHER SIDE.

17:31.184 --> 17:33.120
THERE'S NO REASON
TO BE SO THREATENED--

17:33.186 --> 17:37.090
- WE'RE NOT ABOUT TO HAVE
SCHOOL TAUGHT THAT WAY !
- EXCUSE ME.

17:37.157 --> 17:39.126
I'VE ONLY BEEN TRYING
TO GET ACROSS...

17:39.192 --> 17:42.662
PART OF THE COMPLEXITY
OF OUR SITUATION DOWN HERE.

17:42.729 --> 17:47.100
CULTURES COMING TOGETHER
IN BOTH NEGATIVE
AND POSITIVE WAYS.

17:47.167 --> 17:51.771
IF YOU'RE TALKIN' ABOUT
FOOD AND MUSIC AND ALL,
I HAVE NO PROBLEM WITH THAT.

17:51.838 --> 17:54.441
BUT WHEN YOU START CHANGIN'
WHO DID WHAT TO WHOM--

17:54.507 --> 17:58.010
WE'RE NOT CHANGING ANYTHING.
WE'RE JUST TRYING TO PRESENT
A MORE COMPLETE PICTURE.

17:58.077 --> 18:00.079
THAT'S WHAT'S GOT TO STOP !

18:00.147 --> 18:05.552
THERE'S ENOUGH IGNORANCE
IN THE WORLD WITHOUT US
ENCOURAGING IT IN THE CLASSROOM.

18:05.618 --> 18:08.221
NOW WHO ARE YOU
CALLIN' IGNORANT ?

18:08.288 --> 18:11.224
I HOPE THE SUCKER DOES
DIE, MAN. MESS WITH ME,
THAT'S WHAT YOU GET.

18:11.291 --> 18:13.426
HOSPITAL SAYS THE
OTHER KID'S IN BAD SHAPE.

18:13.493 --> 18:16.163
THE SHOOTER LOCAL ?
DOWN FROM HOUSTON.

18:16.229 --> 18:18.165
THINK HE KNEW
THE GIRL FROM BEFORE.

18:18.231 --> 18:21.601
WE'LL TAKE A STATEMENT
FROM ALL THE G.I.'S
BEFORE THEY GO BACK TO POST.

18:21.668 --> 18:24.737
YOU CAN GET THE STORY
FROM OTIS OVER AT THE CLUB.
OKAY.

18:24.804 --> 18:27.640
ANY POOP ON THE JOHN DOE
WE FOUND OUT THERE TODAY ?

18:27.707 --> 18:32.179
NO, NOTHIN' MUCH.
RANGERS ARE PUTTIN'
BEN WETZEL ON IT.

18:32.245 --> 18:34.547
I'LL CATCH YA LATER.
ALL RIGHT.

18:40.052 --> 18:43.890
[ Phone Ringing,
People Chattering ]

18:45.492 --> 18:48.060
HE'S ONLY 15.
HE'S ABOUT FIVE-FOOT-FIVE--

18:48.127 --> 18:49.762
PILAR ?

18:51.731 --> 18:55.402
- SOMETHING WRONG ?
- THEY'VE GOT MY SON.

18:55.468 --> 18:57.337
- THEY'VE GOT HIM HERE ?
- SOMEBODY CALLED.

18:57.404 --> 19:01.408
SOMETHING ABOUT A HOUSE
THAT WAS BROKEN INTO.
THEY SAY THEY DON'T HAVE HIM--

19:01.474 --> 19:05.678
I KNOW WHAT HE LOOKS LIKE.
I'LL SEE WHAT'S GOING ON.

19:09.282 --> 19:12.685
I WAS, UH--

19:12.752 --> 19:16.356
I WAS REAL SORRY
ABOUT NANDO.

19:18.325 --> 19:20.927
HE WAS A GOOD FELLOW.

19:24.030 --> 19:26.098
WE HAVEN'T TALKED--

19:26.165 --> 19:28.601
WE HAVEN'T TALKED
SINCE HIGH SCHOOL.

19:30.237 --> 19:33.840
YEAH. I'LL GO CHECK
ON YOUR BOY.

19:36.709 --> 19:40.913
RICHIE DIDN'T SAY NOTHIN',
'CAUSE HE DIDN'T WANT
TO GET IN IT, SEE ?

19:40.980 --> 19:44.851
THEN THE NEXT THING I KNOW
THERE'S SHOTS,
AND RICHIE'S DOWN.

19:44.917 --> 19:46.819
IT JUST HAPPENED SO FAST.

19:46.886 --> 19:49.389
WE GOT SOME BOYS
YOU RUN IN EARLIER TODAY ?

19:52.292 --> 19:55.562
THEY TELL ME YOU'RE GOOD
AT FIXIN' THINGS.

20:00.600 --> 20:03.736
YOUR FATHER WAS
A HELL OF A MECHANIC.

20:07.674 --> 20:13.680
YOU KNOW, IF YOU FIGURE
MINIMUM WAGE ON THE TIME
MOST THIEVES SPEND IN JAIL,

20:13.746 --> 20:16.983
THEY COULD HAVE BOUGHT
MOST EVERYTHING
THEY STOLE.

20:17.049 --> 20:21.354
THEY ASKED ME
TO HOOK IT UP FOR THEM.
I DIDN'T STEAL ANYTHING.

20:21.421 --> 20:23.656
I DIDN'T SAY YOU DID.

20:25.425 --> 20:28.361
MY NAME'S SAM,
BY THE WAY.

20:30.730 --> 20:32.765
HE'S ALL YOURS.
ARE YOU OKAY ?

20:32.832 --> 20:34.401
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT THE BIG DEAL IS.

20:34.467 --> 20:37.304
YOU'LL FIND OUT
WHEN I GET YOU HOME.

20:37.370 --> 20:40.307
- THANKS, SAM.
- IT'S NO PROBLEM.

20:43.142 --> 20:45.378
IT WAS GOOD
SEEING YOU AGAIN.

21:11.438 --> 21:15.442
BIG O'S IS THE ONLY PLACE
IN THE COUNTY WHERE
AFRICAN-AMERICAN SOLDIERS ARE--

21:15.508 --> 21:17.710
WELL, THAT THEY FEEL
COMFORTABLE IN, SIR.

21:17.777 --> 21:21.047
HAVE WE HAD TROUBLE
THERE BEFORE ?
FISTFIGHT NOW AND THEN.

21:21.113 --> 21:23.916
THIS TOWN ISN'T MUCH, COLONEL.
THEY DIDN'T COME
FOR VACATION.

21:23.983 --> 21:26.386
NO, SIR, BUT FOR A LOT OF THEM,
IT'S THEIR FIRST TIME
AWAY FROM HOME.

21:26.453 --> 21:30.089
DEALING WITH NEW PEOPLE.
I REMEMBER MY FIRST HITCH.
SUBSTANCE ABUSE ?

21:30.156 --> 21:33.393
YES, SIR, BUT
I WENT THROUGH THE PROGRAM.
I HAVEN'T HAD A DRINK SINCE--

21:33.460 --> 21:36.563
I MEANT ON THE POST
IN GENERAL. HOW ARE YOU
DEALING WITH IT ?

21:36.629 --> 21:39.031
WE THROW A URINE TEST
AT THEM ONCE A MONTH.

21:39.098 --> 21:43.002
RANDOM NUMBERS.
MAYBE 100 PEOPLE
AT A TIME.

21:43.069 --> 21:46.172
LET'S MAKE IT ONCE A WEEK
FOR A WHILE.
NO PROBLEM, SIR.

21:46.238 --> 21:50.977
I SPRINT THE LAST QUARTER MILE.
YOU GENTLEMEN DON'T HAVE TO
KEEP UP IF YOU DON'T CARE TO.

21:51.043 --> 21:52.945
APPRECIATE IT, SIR.

21:57.850 --> 22:00.787
GUY CRACKS WALNUTS
WITH HIS ASSHOLE.

22:00.853 --> 22:03.189
YOU GET THE FEELING
HE DOESN'T WANNA BE HERE ?

22:03.255 --> 22:07.093
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

22:48.568 --> 22:51.571
[ Door Creaking ]

23:01.180 --> 23:02.449
SAM THE MAN.

23:02.515 --> 23:05.852
HEY, BEN.
THANKS FOR COMIN' DOWN.

23:07.654 --> 23:09.722
SO HOW'S BUSINESS ?

23:09.789 --> 23:14.527
BUSINESS IS BOOMIN'.
GOT YOUR DRUGS,
GOT YOUR ILLEGALS.

23:14.594 --> 23:19.832
HAD A SHOOTIN'
THE OTHER NIGHT AT O'S PLACE.
SOLDIER GOT VENTILATED.

23:19.899 --> 23:22.068
I HEAR THEY'RE CLOSIN'
FORT McKENZIE DOWN.

23:22.134 --> 23:24.336
GONNA PULL A LOT OF JOBS
OUTTA THIS COUNTY.

23:24.403 --> 23:28.875
YEAH, WE'LL HAVE FOLKS
SWIMMIN' OVER TO MEXICO
TO WORK IN THE SWEATSHOPS.

23:28.941 --> 23:30.610
[ Sighs ]

23:30.677 --> 23:34.046
THAT THE WORD
ON OUR BOY ?
THIS IS SKINNY.

23:34.113 --> 23:36.783
SKINNY ?

23:36.849 --> 23:39.652
WHEN WE FIND A BODY,
IT'S EITHER
SKINNY OR STINKY,

23:39.719 --> 23:42.021
DEPENDIN' HOW MUCH MEAT
THERE IS ON THE BONES.

23:42.088 --> 23:44.957
IT'S A NICE JOB.

23:45.024 --> 23:49.328
MALE CAUCASIAN,
40 TO 60 YEARS OLD.

23:49.395 --> 23:53.165
FIVE-FOOT-NINE
TO FIVE-ELEVEN.

23:53.232 --> 23:57.637
CHEWED TOBACCO. THEN
WE GOT THE DENTAL RECORDS
AND THE PERSONAL EFFECTS.

23:57.704 --> 23:59.806
IT'S CHARLIE WADE.

23:59.872 --> 24:04.911
THAT BADGE--
DIDN'T COME OUT
OF A CEREAL BOX.

24:04.977 --> 24:06.479
YEAH.

24:09.415 --> 24:11.518
[ Clears Throat ]

24:13.886 --> 24:18.090
LOOK, YOU KNOW
THE POPULAR VERSION
OF HOW HE LEFT TOWN.

24:18.157 --> 24:20.860
EVERYBODY ON THE BORDER
KNOWS THAT STORY.

24:20.927 --> 24:24.096
SO YOU GOT
A CAUSE OF DEATH ?
SKULL WAS INTACT.

24:24.163 --> 24:27.066
THERE'S NO SIGNS
OF TRAUMA ON WHAT
WE FOUND OF HIM.

24:27.133 --> 24:28.835
NOT MUCH TO GO ON.

24:28.901 --> 24:33.940
SO HE COULD HAVE
GONE OUT TO THE POST,
UH, JUST HOPPED THE FENCE,

24:34.006 --> 24:38.878
DUG DOWN INTO THE DIRT
ON THE OLD RIFLE RANGE
AND HAD A HEART ATTACK.

24:42.348 --> 24:45.952
YOU REMEMBER WHAT OLD BUDDY
CARRIED FOR A SIDE ARM ?

24:46.018 --> 24:48.487
COLT PEACEMAKER.

24:48.555 --> 24:50.823
FORTY-FIVE.
HE SWORE BY IT.

24:54.026 --> 24:56.028
WHAT ?

24:56.095 --> 24:57.730
I'S JUST WONDERIN'.

24:59.799 --> 25:02.101
SO IS BUDDY
ON YOUR SHORT LIST ?

25:02.168 --> 25:06.372
IF IT WAS SOME POOR MOJADO
WHO SWAM ACROSS AT NIGHT
AND GOT LOST IN THE BRUSH...

25:06.438 --> 25:08.608
AND STARVED OUT THERE,
I WOULDN'T GO MUCH FURTHER.

25:08.675 --> 25:13.112
BUT THIS IS A FORMERLY
PROMINENT CITIZEN WHO
DISAPPEARED UNDER A CLOUD--

25:13.179 --> 25:15.915
YOU GOT TO INVESTIGATE.
THERE'S NO QUESTION ABOUT IT.

25:15.982 --> 25:22.054
WHAT I WILL DO IS KEEP NAMES
OUT OF IT UNTIL WE GET SOME
ANSWERS OR HIT A DEAD END.

25:22.121 --> 25:24.757
YOU KNOW HOW THE PRESS IS
WHEN THEY GET A HOLD
OF A MURDER STORY,

25:24.824 --> 25:28.527
EVEN IF IT'S 40 YEARS OLD.

25:28.595 --> 25:31.964
YEAH, YEAH, THEY CAN DO
A NUMBER ON YA.

25:34.767 --> 25:40.807
I REMEMBER CHARLIE WADE
COME TO MY FATHER'S
HARDWARE STORE ONCE.

25:40.873 --> 25:43.375
I WAS JUST A LITTLE BOY.

25:43.442 --> 25:45.812
BUT I'D HEARD STORIES ABOUT
HOW HE'D SHOT THIS ONE...

25:45.878 --> 25:48.014
AND HOW HE SHOT THAT ONE.

25:49.548 --> 25:53.152
MAN WINKED AT ME.
I PEED MY PANTS.

25:55.254 --> 25:57.289
WINKED AT ME.

25:57.356 --> 26:00.459
[ Pilar ]
OKAY, WE HAVE THE FIGHT
AGAINST THE SPANISH...

26:00.526 --> 26:06.032
WITH BLOODY CONFLICT FOR
DOZENS OF YEARS 'TIL THEY
ARE FINALLY DEFEATED IN 1821...

26:06.098 --> 26:09.468
AND MEXICAN INDEPENDENCE
IS DECLARED.

26:09.535 --> 26:13.205
ANGLO SETTLERS ARE INVITED
TO COLONIZE THE AREA.

26:13.272 --> 26:16.876
BY THE TIME
THEY BEGIN THE MOVEMENT
AGAINST SANTA ANNA,

26:16.943 --> 26:20.012
THEY OUTNUMBER
THE MEXICANS HERE
BY FOUR TO ONE.

26:20.079 --> 26:24.083
THE WAR BETWEEN MEXICO
AND THE ANGLO FORCES...

26:24.150 --> 26:26.152
ENDS IN 1836...

26:26.218 --> 26:30.022
WITH THE FORMATION
OF THE TEXAS REPUBLIC.

26:30.089 --> 26:35.928
TEXAS JOINS THE
UNITED STATES AS A STATE
WHERE SLAVERY IS LEGAL...

26:35.995 --> 26:40.166
IN 1845 AFTER
THE SO-CALLED MEXICAN WAR,

26:40.232 --> 26:44.236
THEN SECEDES TO JOIN
THE CONFEDERACY IN 1861.

26:44.303 --> 26:48.975
THE CONFEDERACY IS BEATEN,
AND THE REFORMATION PERIOD HERE
IS MARKED...

26:49.041 --> 26:51.678
BY RANGE WARS AND RACE WARS...

26:51.744 --> 26:54.814
AND ALL THIS PARALLELED
BY THE CONSTANT BATTLES...

26:54.881 --> 27:00.386
BETWEEN BOTH THE MEXICAN AND
ANGLO SETTLERS AND THE VARIOUS
INDIAN NATIONS IN THE AREA.

27:00.452 --> 27:02.855
WHAT ARE WE SEEING HERE,
CHET ?

27:02.922 --> 27:06.826
UM, EVERYBODY'S
KILLING EVERYBODY ELSE.

27:15.935 --> 27:20.639
BOY, I ALWAYS WONDERED
WHAT YOU MAYORS DO WHEN
YOU'RE NOT CUTTIN' RIBBONS.

27:21.708 --> 27:22.909
SAM !

27:25.377 --> 27:29.015
PARTNER ! YA CAUGHT ME
PLAYIN' HOOKY.

27:29.081 --> 27:32.651
YEAH, FLOATIN' AROUND OUT HERE,
PLAYIN' HELL WITH THEM BASS.

27:32.719 --> 27:34.754
SOUNDS GREAT.
WHERE DO I SIGN UP ?

27:34.821 --> 27:39.125
YOU BEEN BY YOUR OLD PLACE
LATELY ?
NO.

27:39.191 --> 27:43.129
NEW PEOPLE PAINTED IT
SOME GOD-AWFUL COLOR.

27:43.195 --> 27:48.868
WE FOUND A BODY OUT
BY FORT McKENZIE YESTERDAY.
IT'D BEEN THERE A LONG TIME.

27:48.935 --> 27:52.004
WAS IT DAVY CROCKETT
OR JIM BOWIE ?

27:55.074 --> 27:58.745
YOU RECALL IF CHARLIE WADE
WAS A MASON ?

27:58.811 --> 28:00.612
CHARLIE ?

28:00.679 --> 28:05.051
YEAH, I BELIEVE HE USED
TO GO FOR LODGE MEETINGS
OVER TO LAREDO.

28:05.117 --> 28:08.654
WHAT'S CHARLIE WADE
GOT TO DO WITH YOUR BODY ?

28:08.721 --> 28:12.124
WELL, ALL IT WAS WEARIN' WAS
A BIG, OLD MASONIC RING...

28:12.191 --> 28:14.994
AND A RIO COUNTY
SHERIFF'S BADGE.

28:22.001 --> 28:25.104
YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING ELSE FROM
THAT LAST NIGHT YOU SAW HIM ?

28:25.171 --> 28:28.640
HELL, I'VE TOLD THE STORY
ENOUGH TIMES.

28:28.707 --> 28:32.144
WE WERE JUST IN THE CAR.
HE WAS STEWIN' ABOUT
HIS FIGHT WITH BUDDY...

28:32.211 --> 28:36.415
AS WE DROVE OVER
TO RODERICK BLEDSOE'S.
BLEDSOE ?

28:36.482 --> 28:39.018
HE OWNED THE COLORED
ROADHOUSE BEFORE OTIS.

28:39.085 --> 28:42.421
- HE STILL LIVIN' ?
- NO.

28:42.488 --> 28:47.259
I THINK HIS WIDOW'S
STILL IN THEIR PLACE
IN DARKTOWN, THOUGH.

28:47.326 --> 28:51.130
YOU THINK IT WAS
CHARLIE WADE, HUH ?

28:51.197 --> 28:53.732
FORENSICS PEOPLE
ARE SURE OF IT.

28:55.601 --> 28:59.806
YOU GOT ANY IDEA WHO MIGHT
HAVE PUT HIM THERE ?

28:59.872 --> 29:02.174
BESIDES MY FATHER, I MEAN.

29:03.642 --> 29:06.145
THERE'S NO CALL
FOR THAT, SAM.

29:06.212 --> 29:08.948
WADE MADE HISSELF A PILE
OF ENEMIES OVER THE YEARS.

29:09.015 --> 29:10.983
YEAH, AND BUDDY
WAS ONE OF 'EM.

29:11.050 --> 29:16.288
WITH THE DEDICATION TOMORROW,
THIS IS A HELL OF A TIME
TO BRING UP OLD BUSINESS.

29:16.355 --> 29:19.959
PEOPLE HAVE WORKED THIS WHOLE
BIG THING UP AROUND MY FATHER.

29:20.026 --> 29:23.329
IF IT'S BUILT ON A CRIME,
THEY DESERVE TO KNOW.

29:23.395 --> 29:26.398
I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU MIGHT WANT
TO BELIEVE HE COULDN'T DO IT.

29:26.465 --> 29:29.501
I UNDERSTAND WHY YOU MIGHT
WANT TO THINK HE COULD.

29:38.444 --> 29:41.313
THANKS FOR YOUR TIME,
HOLLIS.

29:42.448 --> 29:45.151
HEY, LOOK AT ALL THIS,
WILL YA ?

29:47.119 --> 29:49.388
[ Tackle Box Rattles ]
TACKLE, BOAT !

29:51.490 --> 29:53.659
ALL JUST TO CATCH
A LITTLE OLD FISH,

29:53.725 --> 29:56.829
MINDIN' HIS OWN BUSINESS
DOWN IN THE BOTTOM OF THE LAKE.

30:00.232 --> 30:04.103
HARDLY SEEMS WORTH
THE EFFORT, DOES IT, SAM ?

30:07.907 --> 30:10.576
[ Cliff ]
SO YOU KNEW
THIS YOUNG MAN BEFORE ?

30:10.642 --> 30:13.779
FROM BACK IN HOUSTON.
WE BOTH COME UP
ON FIFTH STREET.

30:13.846 --> 30:16.115
[ Woman ]
DID YOU KNOW HE WAS
GONNA BE THERE LAST NIGHT ?

30:16.182 --> 30:19.118
IF I HAD, I WOULDN'T
HAVE GONE IN.

30:19.185 --> 30:21.921
AND YOU AND
PRIVATE GRAVES WERE...

30:21.988 --> 30:24.256
WE WERE JUST DANCIN'.

30:24.323 --> 30:26.492
WE'RE NOT RUNNIN'
A DATIN' SERVICE HERE,
PRIVATE.

30:26.558 --> 30:30.196
I KNOW THAT, SERGEANT.
WE WERE JUST DANCIN'.

30:30.262 --> 30:32.364
THERE WAS
A BUNCH OF US THERE.

30:32.431 --> 30:36.568
SHADOW-- SHADOW JUST COME
DOWN LOOKIN' FOR TROUBLE.

30:36.635 --> 30:40.339
I DON'T LIKE
TO GET INVOLVED WITH
THE PERSONAL LIFE OF SOLDIERS,

30:40.406 --> 30:42.608
BUT WHEN IT INTERFERES
WITH THE TRAINING HERE--

30:42.674 --> 30:46.112
SHADOW JUST GETS CRAZY.

30:46.178 --> 30:49.648
SERGEANT, HOW IS RICHIE DOIN'--
PRIVATE GRAVES ?

30:49.715 --> 30:54.286
HE'LL LIVE.
HE'LL BE TRANSFERRED TO FORT SAM
AS SOON AS HE'S STABILIZED.

30:54.353 --> 30:59.125
HE'LL PROBABLY BE GETTING
A MEDICAL DISCHARGE.

30:59.191 --> 31:02.628
WILL THIS GO
ON MY RECORD ?

31:02.694 --> 31:05.764
THE INCIDENT WILL BE NOTED.

31:05.831 --> 31:08.367
BUT IF IT HAPPENED
THE WAY YOU SAY IT DID,

31:08.434 --> 31:10.836
THERE HASN'T BEEN
AN INFRACTION.

31:10.903 --> 31:12.371
THANK YOU, SERGEANT.

31:12.438 --> 31:15.141
YOU'RE DISMISSED.
THANK YOU, SERGEANT.

31:26.718 --> 31:29.721
YOU SPOIL 'EM, CLIFF.
YOU DON'T BELIEVE HER ?

31:29.788 --> 31:32.691
LET'S JUST SAY THAT WASN'T
MUCH OF AN INTERROGATION.

31:32.758 --> 31:35.461
I'M THE ONE IN CHARGE
OF HER SORRY ASS,
AND QUITE FRANKLY--

31:35.527 --> 31:39.365
I DON'T WANT TO GIVE HER
THE THIRD DEGREE BECAUSE
HER EX-BOYFRIEND IS A THUG.

31:39.431 --> 31:41.667
SHE'S PULLED HERSELF
OUT OF A PRETTY ROUGH
NEIGHBORHOOD.

31:41.733 --> 31:45.938
IF SHE ISN'T CAREFUL,
SHE'S GONNA SLIDE
RIGHT BACK INTO IT.

31:46.005 --> 31:48.174
[ Beeping ]

31:48.240 --> 31:50.376
[ Car Approaches, Stops ]

31:54.746 --> 31:56.949
[ Car Door Closes ]

32:01.853 --> 32:04.623
MRS. BLEDSOE ?
THAT'S ME.

32:07.126 --> 32:09.228
I'M SHERIFF DEEDS.

32:10.529 --> 32:14.133
SHERIFF DEEDS IS DEAD, HONEY.
YOU JUST SHERIFF JUNIOR.

32:15.401 --> 32:17.836
YEAH, THAT'S
THE STORY OF MY LIFE.

32:17.903 --> 32:21.273
YOU EVER PLAY ONE OF THESE ?

32:23.109 --> 32:25.444
YEAH, I'VE SEEN 'EM.

32:25.511 --> 32:30.482
DON'T EVER START UP
ON 'EM, 'CAUSE ONCE
YOU DO, YOU CAN'T STOP.

32:30.549 --> 32:35.154
I TELL MYSELF I'M JUST
GONNA PLAY THREE LITTLE GAMES
AFTER BREAKFAST.

32:35.221 --> 32:39.992
AND HERE I AM
WITH HALF THE DAY GONE.

32:40.059 --> 32:44.563
YOU MIND IF I ASK YOU
A FEW QUESTIONS ABOUT
YOUR HUSBAND RODERICK ?

32:44.630 --> 32:50.036
I AIN'T GONNA SAY
NOTHIN' BAD ABOUT THE MAN,
BUT YOU CAN ASK AWAY.

32:50.102 --> 32:52.938
HE HAD THE CLUB OUT
ON THE OLD TRAIL ROAD ?

32:53.005 --> 32:56.142
WE RUN THAT CLUB
FOR OVER 20 YEARS.

32:56.208 --> 32:59.045
GIVE IT OVER
TO OTIS PAYNE IN...

32:59.111 --> 33:02.548
1967, APRIL.

33:02.614 --> 33:05.617
THEN YOU MUST
REMEMBER SHERIFF WADE ?

33:05.684 --> 33:07.419
THEM DAYS,

33:07.486 --> 33:11.023
YOU DEAL WITH SHERIFF WADE
OR YOU DIDN'T DEAL.

33:11.090 --> 33:17.263
FIRST OF THE MONTH
EVERY MONTH, HE REMIND YOU
OF WHO YOU REALLY WORKIN' FOR.

33:17.329 --> 33:19.531
SO HE SQUEEZED MONEY
OUT OF YOU ?

33:19.598 --> 33:22.868
WASN'T LEGAL
TO SELL LIQUOR
IN A GLASS BACK THEN,

33:22.934 --> 33:27.005
UNLESS YOU WAS A CLUB, SEE ?

33:27.073 --> 33:28.607
RODERICK USED TO SAY,

33:28.674 --> 33:31.910
"BUY YOURSELF A GLASS,
GET A FREE MEMBERSHIP."

33:31.977 --> 33:33.779
[ Chuckling ]

33:33.845 --> 33:38.016
THAT SHERIFF WADE,
HE COULD CLOSE YOU DOWN ANYTIME.

33:38.084 --> 33:40.619
AND MY FATHER ?

33:40.686 --> 33:43.689
SHERIFF BUDDY WAS
A DIFFERENT STORY.

33:43.755 --> 33:47.493
LONG AS RODERICK THROW
HIS WEIGHT THE RIGHT WAY
AT ELECTION DAY,

33:47.559 --> 33:49.561
MAKE SURE ALL THE COLORED
COME OUT TO VOTE,

33:49.628 --> 33:52.231
THROW A BARBECUE FOR THE
RIGHT FOLKS NOW AND THEN,

33:52.298 --> 33:55.234
SHERIFF BUDDY
KEPT TO HIS WORD.

33:55.301 --> 34:00.506
THAT SHERIFF WADE, THOUGH,
HE COULD GET UGLY.

34:00.572 --> 34:03.309
AND PEOPLE DIDN'T COMPLAIN,
HUH ?

34:03.375 --> 34:06.745
NOT IF YOU WAS COLORED
OR MEXICAN.

34:06.812 --> 34:09.181
NOT IF YOU WANTED
TO KEEP BREATHING.

34:09.248 --> 34:12.618
I REMEMBER
THE LAST TIME I SEEN HIM
BEFORE HE GO ON MISSIN'.

34:12.684 --> 34:15.154
HE COME FUSSIN'
AROUND OUR PLACE.

34:15.221 --> 34:18.857
HE USED TO COME IN
WHILST WE WAS IN FULL SWING,

34:18.924 --> 34:21.193
MAKIN' EVERYBODY NERVOUS.

34:21.260 --> 34:24.763
HAD HIM A SMILE
LIKE THE GRIM REAPER.

34:24.830 --> 34:27.899
HE USED TO SIT THERE
WITH HIS HAND
ON HIS OLD GUN,

34:27.966 --> 34:32.371
ACTIN' THE KINGFISH
WITH EVERYBODY.

34:34.806 --> 34:37.976
OTIS PAYNE COME TO WORK
FOR US ABOUT THAT TIME.

34:38.043 --> 34:43.382
[ Chuckles ]
AND THAT BOY
HAD HIM SOME ATTITUDE.

34:43.449 --> 34:45.384
* SHAKE, RATTLE AND ROLL *

34:45.451 --> 34:48.053
* SHAKE, RATTLE AND ROLL *

34:48.120 --> 34:50.889
* SHAKE, RATTLE AND ROLL *

34:50.956 --> 34:56.362
* WELL, YOU WON'T DO NOTHIN'
TO SAVE YOUR DOGGONE SOUL *

34:56.428 --> 35:00.166
* SHAKE, RATTLE AND ROLL *

35:02.868 --> 35:05.637
POUR IT.

35:05.704 --> 35:07.038
WHAT ?

35:07.105 --> 35:09.175
POUR IT !

35:19.951 --> 35:21.987
[ Liquid Pouring ]
I KNOW YOU ?

35:22.053 --> 35:25.624
- NAME'S OTIS.
- OTIS WHAT ?

35:26.992 --> 35:31.563
PAYNE.
THEY CALL ME "O."

35:31.630 --> 35:34.233
ONE OF
CLEROE PAYNE'S BOYS ?

35:34.300 --> 35:35.501
UH-HUH.

35:35.567 --> 35:39.205
I SENT YOUR DADDY
TO THE FARM ONCE.

35:39.271 --> 35:41.072
YEAH, I KNOW THAT.

35:41.139 --> 35:43.209
WHY YOU THINK THAT WAS ?

35:44.510 --> 35:49.080
SOME CROP NEEDED PICKIN'.
THE MAN WAS SHORTHANDED.

35:49.147 --> 35:52.351
AS I REMEMBER IT WAS BECAUSE
HE HAD A SASSY MOUTH ON HIM.

35:52.418 --> 35:55.321
MUST RUN IN THE FAMILY.

35:55.387 --> 36:00.125
YOU WOULDN'T BE RUNNIN'
NUMBERS OUT OF THIS CLUB,
WOULD YA, SON ?

36:00.192 --> 36:02.228
RUNNIN' NUMBERS
IS ILLEGAL, SIR.

36:02.294 --> 36:07.132
RUNNIN' NUMBERS
WITHOUT I KNOW ABOUT IT
IS BOTH ILLEGAL AND UNHEALTHY.

36:07.199 --> 36:10.569
YOU REMEMBER THAT.

36:10.636 --> 36:12.671
WHOA, SON.
YOU'RE NOT FINISHED.

36:12.738 --> 36:15.974
- POUR HIS.
- I PREFER IT IN A BOTTLE.

36:16.041 --> 36:17.676
SHUT UP, HOLLIS.

36:23.782 --> 36:25.751
HOW COME YOU DON'T
LOOK FAMILIAR ?

36:25.817 --> 36:29.955
I BEEN AWAY,
UP TO HOUSTON.
HOUSTON ?

36:30.021 --> 36:33.525
I HEAR THEY LET YOU BOYS
RUN WILD UP THERE.

36:33.592 --> 36:35.594
OH, LOOK WHAT YOU DONE NOW.

36:35.661 --> 36:38.897
BETTER GET SOMETHING
TO WIPE IT UP, SON.

36:42.401 --> 36:44.936
YOU SPILT IT.
MAYBE YOU SHOULD WIPE IT UP.

36:52.678 --> 36:57.516
I TOLD YOU TO DO SOMETHING.
YOU GONNA HOP TO IT OR ARE
WE GONNA HAVE A PROBLEM ?

36:59.818 --> 37:04.022
DON'T WANNA TURN TAIL IN
FRONT OF YOUR PEOPLE, HUH ?

37:04.089 --> 37:05.357
I UNDERSTAND.

37:07.526 --> 37:12.097
- [ Woman Screams ]
- COME ON, HOUSTON.
GIVE IT A TRY.

37:12.163 --> 37:15.000
COME TO PAPA.

37:15.066 --> 37:18.003
UH, DON'T MIND HIM, SHERIFF !

37:18.069 --> 37:22.173
THE BOY IS A BIT SLOW IS ALL.
HE DON'T MEAN NOTHIN' BY IT.

37:22.240 --> 37:25.844
THAT THE PROBLEM, SON ?
YOU SLOW ?

37:25.911 --> 37:30.048
OTIS. APOLOGIZE
TO THE SHERIFF.

37:30.115 --> 37:34.820
[ Chuckles ]
SHERIFF, YOU GOT HIM
TOO SCARED TO PEEP.

37:34.886 --> 37:38.056
MAYBE IF YOU'D
PUT THAT GUN UP ?

37:38.123 --> 37:39.458
YOU TELLIN' ME WHAT TO DO ?

37:39.525 --> 37:41.293
NO, SHERIFF, I'M JUST--

37:41.360 --> 37:44.796
IS THAT WHISKEY IN THEM GLASSES
ON THE BAR ?

37:44.863 --> 37:48.567
RODERICK, I'M GONNA
HAVE TO CITE YOU
FOR VIOLATION OF STATE LAW.

37:48.634 --> 37:51.570
THIS IS A CLUB, SHERIFF.
YOU BEEN HERE.

37:51.637 --> 37:55.273
ALL YOU PEOPLE BETTER
CLEAR OUTTA HERE NOW.

38:03.382 --> 38:06.985
YOU LEARN HOW TO ACT
YOUR PLACE, SON.

38:07.052 --> 38:09.020
THIS ISN'T HOUSTON.

38:13.191 --> 38:16.495
'COURSE, I WAS YOUNG...

38:16.562 --> 38:19.831
AND FULL OF BEANS
BACK THEN.

38:19.898 --> 38:24.035
I DIDN'T UNDERSTAND THE SPOT
I WAS PUTTIN' RODERICK IN.

38:30.275 --> 38:34.880
AND THAT WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM ?

38:34.946 --> 38:38.517
I THINK HE CAME IN
ONE MORE TIME.

38:38.584 --> 38:41.820
UH, WITH HOLLIS AND, UH--
NO, NO.

38:41.887 --> 38:46.558
YOUR DADDY WASN'T WITH HIM.
MADE THEIR MONTHLY PICKUP.

38:46.625 --> 38:51.863
RODERICK WASN'T IN,
SO I KEPT MY MOUTH SHUT
AND HANDED OVER THAT ENVELOPE.

38:51.930 --> 38:54.366
AND THAT WAS THE NIGHT
HE DISAPPEARED ?

38:56.234 --> 38:59.070
COULD HAVE BEEN.

39:05.944 --> 39:08.313
YOU OWN A GUN ?

39:08.380 --> 39:10.081
BACK THEN ?

39:10.148 --> 39:12.818
NO.

39:12.884 --> 39:14.085
HOW ABOUT RODERICK ?

39:14.152 --> 39:19.825
OH, HE KEPT A BIG OLD PIECE
BACK BEHIND THE BAR,

39:19.891 --> 39:22.894
JUST SO FOLKS
KNEW IT WAS THERE.

39:22.961 --> 39:28.734
I DON'T KEEP ONE HERE NOW.
DON'T MUCH CARE FOR 'EM.

39:28.800 --> 39:30.836
AND WHEN MY FATHER
WAS SHERIFF ?

39:30.902 --> 39:34.540
- WHAT ABOUT HIM ?
- WHAT WAS YOUR DEAL WITH HIM ?

39:37.843 --> 39:40.546
[ Sighs ]

39:40.612 --> 39:44.683
BUDDY WAS MORE A PART
OF THE BIG PICTURE.

39:44.750 --> 39:47.586
COUNTY POLITICAL MACHINE.

39:47.653 --> 39:51.056
CHAMBER OF COMMERCE.
ZONING BOARD.

39:51.122 --> 39:56.161
IF I KEPT THOSE PEOPLE HAPPY,
HE WAS PRETTY MUCH ON MY SIDE.

39:56.227 --> 40:00.031
WHENEVER SOMEBODY THOUGHT
OF STARTIN' UP A NEW BAR
FOR THE BLACK FOLKS,

40:00.098 --> 40:03.068
THEY'D BE, UH--

40:03.134 --> 40:05.336
HOW SHOULD I SAY THIS ?

40:05.403 --> 40:08.406
THEY'D BE
OFFICIALLY DISCOURAGED.

40:08.474 --> 40:12.077
HE EVER ACCEPT CASH
FOR A FAVOR ?

40:19.184 --> 40:24.756
I DON'T RECALL
A PRISONER EVER DIED
IN YOUR DADDY'S CUSTODY.

40:26.692 --> 40:32.330
I DON'T RECALL
A MAN IN THIS COUNTY--
BLACK, WHITE, MEXICAN--

40:32.397 --> 40:35.100
WHO'D HESITATE
FOR A MINUTE...

40:35.166 --> 40:40.472
BEFORE THEY'D
CALL ON BUDDY DEEDS
TO SOLVE A PROBLEM.

40:40.539 --> 40:43.709
MORE THAN THAT,

40:43.775 --> 40:45.777
I WOULDN'T CARE TO SAY.

40:47.746 --> 40:51.550
I'M SUPPOSED TO TELL
MY FRIENDS THEY'RE
TOO LOW CLASS TO HANG WITH ?

40:51.617 --> 40:53.118
COME ON, AMADO.

40:53.184 --> 40:54.786
JUST BECAUSE I'M NOT LIKE
LITTLE MISS HONOR ROLL ?

40:54.853 --> 40:56.588
LEAVE YOUR SISTER
OUT OF THIS.

40:56.655 --> 40:59.157
YOU AND THOSE
TEACHERS IN THAT DUMP,
YOUR STORY'S OVER.

40:59.224 --> 41:01.727
SO YOU DON'T WANT
ANYBODY ELSE TO HAVE FUN.
YOU JERK !

41:01.793 --> 41:03.729
I'M NOT TALKING TO YOU.
YOU DON'T HAVE ANY FRIENDS.

41:03.795 --> 41:06.632
WHO'D WANT TO BE FRIENDS
WITH PACHUCO WANNA-BES ?

41:06.698 --> 41:08.266
I DON'T PRETEND I CAME
OVER ON THE MAYFLOWER.

41:08.333 --> 41:11.269
AND THOSE STUPID GIRLS
WHO HANG OUT WITH THEM.
SHUT UP !

41:11.336 --> 41:15.240
JOANIE OROZCO'S TELLING
THE WHOLE SCHOOL SHE'S
IN LOVE WITH SANTO GUERRA.

41:15.306 --> 41:17.075
- SO ?
- IT'S PATHETIC.

41:17.142 --> 41:19.745
YOU CAN'T BE
DESPERATELY IN LOVE
WHEN YOU'RE 14 YEARS OLD.

41:19.811 --> 41:22.447
NOT IF YOU HAVE
HALF A BRAIN.

41:22.514 --> 41:25.684
OF COURSE YOU CAN.
WHAT ?

41:25.751 --> 41:29.721
IT'S GOT NOTHIN' TO DO
WITH BEING SMART.

41:29.788 --> 41:32.223
IT'S ANCIENT
GODDAMN HISTORY, DANNY.

41:32.290 --> 41:36.394
1963, THEY DAM UP THE NORTH
BRANCH TO MAKE LAKE PESCADERO.

41:36.461 --> 41:38.296
A WHOLE LITTLE TOWN
DISAPPEARS.

41:38.363 --> 41:41.933
- A SQUATTER'S TOWN !
- PEOPLE HAD BEEN LIVING
IN PERDIDO FOR 100 YEARS.

41:42.000 --> 41:44.636
MEXICANS AND CHICANOS
ARE DEPORTED, EVICTED,

41:44.703 --> 41:49.040
MOVED FORCIBLY OUT OF
THEIR HOUSES BY OUR LOCAL HERO,
BUDDY DEEDS, AND HIS DEPARTMENT.

41:49.107 --> 41:50.842
THERE WAS A BILL
FROM THE STATE LEGISLATURE.

41:50.909 --> 41:54.079
FAMILIES WERE
SPLIT APART, JORGE.
A COMMUNITY WAS DESTROYED.

41:54.145 --> 41:58.183
WHO ENDS UP WITH
LAKEFRONT PROPERTY BOUGHT FOR
A FRACTION OF THE MARKET PRICE ?

41:58.249 --> 42:03.521
BUDDY DEEDS,
SHERIFF OF RIO COUNTY, AND
HIS CHIEF DEPUTY, HOLLIS POGUE.

42:03.589 --> 42:06.257
YOU FINISHED ?

42:06.324 --> 42:08.359
LOOK, I'M NOT
AFTER YOU, SAM.

42:08.426 --> 42:11.963
I THINK PEOPLE IN TOWN
OUGHT TO KNOW THE FULL STORY
ON BUDDY DEEDS.

42:14.666 --> 42:17.703
THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

42:20.471 --> 42:22.140
I DON'T SEE WHAT
THE BIG DEAL IS.

42:22.207 --> 42:24.776
GO BACK OVER,
TALK TO THE MAN
AND BURY THE HATCHET.

42:24.843 --> 42:28.246
WHY SHOULD I BE THE ONE ?
HE'S HAD ALMOST 40 YEARS.
I HAVEN'T HEARD A WORD FROM HIM.

42:28.313 --> 42:32.884
- HE WAS PROBABLY EMBARRASSED.
- OTIS PAYNE WAS NEVER
EMBARRASSED IN HIS LIFE.

42:32.951 --> 42:35.286
- DAD.
- DEL, YOU WERE EIGHT
WHEN HE LEFT.

42:35.353 --> 42:39.190
HE DIDN'T LEAVE.
HE MOVED THREE HOUSES DOWN WITH
ONE OF MY MOTHER'S BEST FRIENDS.

42:39.257 --> 42:40.859
DAD ?

42:40.926 --> 42:43.161
"HEY, DELMORE,
WHERE'S YOUR DADDY ?"

42:43.228 --> 42:46.131
THIS GODFORSAKEN TOWN.
EVERYBODY IN EVERYBODY ELSE'S
BUSINESS.

42:46.197 --> 42:48.967
AND EVERYBODY LOVED OTIS.
BIG O.

42:49.034 --> 42:53.538
ALWAYS THERE WITH A SMILE
OR A LOAN OR A FREE DRINK.

42:53.605 --> 42:57.175
- DAD, CAN I TALK
TO YOU ABOUT TRACK ?
- PEOPLE CHANGE.

42:57.242 --> 42:59.177
- NOT THAT MUCH.
- I TALKED TO THE TRACK COACH.

42:59.244 --> 43:01.680
WE ALREADY HAD THIS OUT.
NEXT YEAR IF YOUR GRADES
ARE HIGHER.

43:01.747 --> 43:05.216
-I HAVE A "B" AVERAGE.
-HOW MANY "B" AVERAGES DO YOU
THINK THEY TAKE AT WEST POINT ?

43:05.283 --> 43:09.254
WE'RE STUCK HERE
FOR THREE YEARS.
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO SEE HIM.

43:09.320 --> 43:10.822
NO. WE DON'T.

43:21.199 --> 43:23.802
GET OFF THE PHONE, ENRIQUE.
WE'VE GOT PEOPLE WAITING.

43:23.869 --> 43:25.170
Â¿ MAMI ?

43:29.274 --> 43:31.276
THESE ONES COMING OVER ARE
GETTING STUPIDER EVERY YEAR.

43:31.342 --> 43:33.444
MAYBE YOU'RE JUST
GETTIN' LESS PATIENT.

43:33.511 --> 43:37.615
IF THEY'RE GOING TO
SURVIVE HERE, THEY HAVE
TO KNOW HOW TO WORK.

43:37.683 --> 43:41.152
IF YOU HIRE ILLEGALS,
WHAT DO YOU EXPECT ?

43:41.219 --> 43:43.421
NOBODY'S ILLEGAL
IN MY CAFE.

43:43.488 --> 43:47.425
THEY'VE GOT GREEN CARDS.
THEY'VE GOT RELATIVES
WHO WERE BORN HERE.

43:47.492 --> 43:50.228
IF THEY ONLY HAD
A LITTLE COMMON SENSE,
I'D BE VERY HAPPY.

43:50.295 --> 43:54.032
MAYBE IF YOU TOOK
MORE TIME TRAINING THEM,
YOU WOULDN'T HAVE THIS--

43:54.099 --> 43:58.003
YOU COME HERE TO TEACH ME
HOW TO RUN MY BUSINESS ?

44:05.176 --> 44:09.380
I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU WANTED TO TAKE
A TRIP SOUTH WITH US.

44:09.447 --> 44:13.551
MAYBE SEE WHERE YOU GREW UP ?
WHY WOULD I WANT
TO GO THERE ?

44:13.618 --> 44:16.187
YOU MUST BE CURIOUS
HOW IT'S CHANGED.

44:16.254 --> 44:19.657
AMADO IS INTO THIS
BIG TEJANO ROOTS THING.

44:19.725 --> 44:23.194
I'VE NEVER BEEN FURTHER
THAN CIUDAD LEON.

44:23.261 --> 44:27.565
YOU WANNA SEE MEXICANS ?
OPEN YOUR EYES
AND LOOK AROUND YOU.

44:27.632 --> 44:30.201
WE'RE UP TO OUR EARS
IN THEM.

44:31.569 --> 44:35.774
MAMI, HOW OLD WERE YOU...

44:35.841 --> 44:38.343
WHEN MY FATHER DIED ?

44:38.409 --> 44:40.011
HE WAS KILLED.

44:40.078 --> 44:42.247
RIGHT.
WHEN HE WAS KILLED.

44:43.915 --> 44:47.385
A LITTLE OLDER
THAN PALOMA IS NOW.

44:47.452 --> 44:50.889
HOW COME YOU NEVER
GOT MARRIED AGAIN ?

44:50.956 --> 44:53.992
IT JUST DIDN'T HAPPEN.

44:54.059 --> 44:58.463
THERE MUST HAVE
BEEN SOMEBODY.

44:58.529 --> 45:01.599
I WAS TOO BUSY.

45:01.666 --> 45:04.936
MAMI, NOBODY IS TOO BUSY.

45:05.003 --> 45:09.274
MAYBE NOW.
IT WAS DIFFERENT BACK THEN.

45:09.340 --> 45:12.710
I HAD TO DO ALL THE SHOPPING,
ALL THE COOKING.

45:12.778 --> 45:18.216
WHAT DO I NEED SOME CHULO
WITH GREASE UNDER HIS NAILS
TO DRINK UP THE PROFIT ?

45:18.283 --> 45:19.317
THANK YOU.

45:19.384 --> 45:20.618
I DON'T MEAN FERNANDO.

45:20.685 --> 45:24.222
MAMI,WHEN I BROUGHT HIM HOME,
THOSE WERE YOUR EXACT WORDS.

45:24.289 --> 45:26.724
SOME CHULO WITH GREASE
UNDER HIS NAILS.

45:26.792 --> 45:31.496
- I NEVER SAID THAT.
- YOU MADE IT PRETTY DAMN
CLEAR. YOU THOUGHT HE WAS
NOBODY.

45:31.562 --> 45:33.899
I FELT YOU COULD
DO BETTER FOR YOURSELF.

45:33.965 --> 45:36.567
WHAT ? WHAT ?

45:36.634 --> 45:39.838
BECOME A NUN ?
YOU DIDN'T EVEN WANT ME
TO GO OUT WITH ANGLOS.

45:39.905 --> 45:43.741
I NEVER SAID THAT.
IT WAS JUST THAT BOY.

45:43.809 --> 45:45.310
"THAT BOY."

45:45.376 --> 45:49.347
MAMI, SAY HIS NAME,
FOR CHRIST'S SAKES.

45:52.050 --> 45:56.988
YOU PEOPLE ARE STEALING FROM ME.
i ENTIENDE ! i ROBANDOME !

46:01.759 --> 46:03.161
Â¿ LO MADRE ?

46:03.228 --> 46:04.963
MM-HMM.

46:05.030 --> 46:06.464
LO SIENTO.

46:08.366 --> 46:10.802
NOW, I'M AS LIBERAL
AS THE NEXT GUY.

46:10.869 --> 46:13.238
IF THE NEXT GUY
IS A REDNECK.

46:13.304 --> 46:19.177
BUT I GOTTA SAY,
I THINK THERE'S SOMETHING
TO THIS COLD CLIMATE BUSINESS.

46:19.244 --> 46:24.315
I MEAN, YOU GO TO THE BEACH,
WHAT DO YOU DO ?

46:24.382 --> 46:29.120
DRINK A FEW BEERS,
WAIT FOR THAT FISH
TO FLOP UP ON THE SAND.

46:29.187 --> 46:32.757
CAN'T BUILD
NO CIVILIZATION THAT WAY.

46:32.824 --> 46:37.062
BUT YOU GOT
A COLD WINTER COMIN' ON,
YOU GOT TO PLAN AHEAD.

46:37.128 --> 46:40.065
THAT GIVES YOUR OLD
CEREBRAL CORTEX A WORKOUT.
[ Bottle Top Popping ]

46:40.131 --> 46:42.233
GOOD THING YOU WERE
BORN DOWN HERE THEN.

46:42.300 --> 46:47.839
YOU JOKE ABOUT IT, SAM,
BUT WE ARE IN A STATE OF CRISIS.

46:47.906 --> 46:49.875
THE LINES OF DEMARCATION
ARE GETTIN' FUZZY.

46:49.941 --> 46:54.712
TO RUN A SUCCESSFUL CIVILIZATION
YOU HAVE GOT TO HAVE
YOUR LINES OF DEMARCATION...

46:54.779 --> 46:58.316
BETWEEN RIGHT AND WRONG,
BETWEEN THIS 'UN AND THAT 'UN.

46:58.383 --> 47:03.288
YOUR DADDY UNDERSTOOD THAT.
HE WAS A--
WHAT DO YOU CALL IT ?

47:03.354 --> 47:06.757
A REFEREE FOR THIS
DAMN MENUDO WE GOT DOWN HERE.

47:06.824 --> 47:10.862
HE UNDERSTOOD HOW
MOST FOLKS DON'T WANT
THEIR SALT AND SUGAR...

47:10.929 --> 47:12.830
IN THE SAME JAR.

47:12.898 --> 47:18.236
BOY, YOU MIX DRINKS
AS BAD AS YOU MIX METAPHORS,
YOU'D BE OUT OF A JOB.

47:18.303 --> 47:21.239
YOU'RE THE LAST WHITE SHERIFF
THIS TOWN'S GONNA SEE.

47:21.306 --> 47:25.710
HOLLIS RETIRES NEXT YEAR.
JORGE GUERRA'S GONNA TAKE OVER.

47:25.776 --> 47:28.546
THIS IS IT RIGHT HERE, SAM.

47:28.613 --> 47:31.116
THIS BAR IS THE LAST STAND.

47:31.182 --> 47:34.819
SE HABLA AMERICAN,
GODDAMN IT.

47:34.886 --> 47:38.990
EVEN IN HERE
IT'S SLIDIN' AWAY. TSK.

47:39.057 --> 47:43.361
TAKE THAT PAIR OVER THERE
IN THE CORNER.

47:43.428 --> 47:47.265
PLACE LIKE THIS,
20 YEARS AGO,

47:47.332 --> 47:49.400
BUDDY'D BEEN ON THEM TWO.

47:49.467 --> 47:52.637
HE'D HAVE WENT OVER THERE
AND GIVE THEM A WARNING.

47:52.703 --> 47:57.976
NOT THAT HE HAD IT IN
FOR THE COLORED, BUT JUST
AS A KIND OF SAFETY TIP.

47:59.177 --> 48:01.879
YEAH, I BET HE WOULD.

48:01.947 --> 48:04.782
DAY THAT MAN DIED,

48:04.849 --> 48:07.885
THEY BROKE THE GODDAMN MOLD.

48:14.625 --> 48:16.627
SERIOUSLY.
"SERIOUSLY" ?

48:16.694 --> 48:19.931
I THINK WE SHOULD
GET MARRIED.

48:19.998 --> 48:21.066
WE'VE BEEN
THROUGH THIS BEFORE.

48:21.132 --> 48:22.968
WE SHOULD JUST DO IT.

48:23.034 --> 48:26.938
AND IF I GET TRANSFERRED
TO A DIFFERENT POST ?
GERMANY OR KOREA ?

48:27.005 --> 48:30.875
- I'D ASK FOR A TRANSFER TOO.
- WHICH THEY ARE MOST LIKELY
TO TURN DOWN.

48:30.942 --> 48:33.278
I'D QUIT THE ARMY FOR YOU,
IF IT CAME TO THAT.

48:33.344 --> 48:36.614
[ Chuckles ]
YOU KNOW, YOU ARE SOMETHIN'.

48:36.681 --> 48:41.186
MAN'S GONNA RETIRE IN TWO YEARS,
AND HE OFFERS TO QUIT.

48:41.252 --> 48:44.422
BIG GODDAMN DEAL.
[ Sam ]
EXCUSE ME.

48:44.489 --> 48:48.226
SHERIFF. HI.
THIS IS SERGEANT--

48:48.293 --> 48:50.561
THIS IS PRISCILLA WORTH.

48:50.628 --> 48:53.999
SHERIFF DEEDS WAS WITH US
ON OUR ARCHAEOLOGICAL FIND
YESTERDAY.

48:54.065 --> 48:56.001
IT TRUE THEY GONNA BUILD
A SHOPPING MALL OUT THERE ?

48:56.067 --> 49:00.238
IF CERTAIN PEOPLE
HAVE THEIR WAY,
IT'S GONNA BE A NEW JAIL.

49:00.305 --> 49:02.907
DAMN. THEY CLOSIN' DOWN
MILITARY LEFT AND RIGHT...

49:02.974 --> 49:07.145
AND PUTTIN' UP JAILS
LIKE 7-ELEVEN STORES.

49:07.212 --> 49:09.547
SAY, DO EITHER OF YOU
HAVE ANY IDEA...

49:09.614 --> 49:13.551
WHEN THEY STOPPED USIN'
THAT SITE AS A RIFLE RANGE ?

49:13.618 --> 49:17.788
FORT MCKENZIE STOPPED TRAINING
INFANTRY THERE IN THE LATE '50s.

49:17.855 --> 49:22.227
IT WAS JUST A PLAYGROUND
FOR THE JACKRABBITS 'TIL THEY
GAVE IT TO THE COUNTY LAST YEAR.

49:22.293 --> 49:24.762
YOU KNOW WHO IT WAS
THEY DUG UP ?

49:24.829 --> 49:28.066
I'M NOT FOR SURE YET.

49:28.133 --> 49:30.435
BUT I KIND OF
WISH THEY HADN'T.

49:35.306 --> 49:37.508
ES MUY LINDO,
SU COCHE, SENORA.

49:37.575 --> 49:41.612
IN ENGLISH, ENRIQUE.
THIS IS THE UNITED STATES.

49:41.679 --> 49:43.648
WE SPEAK ENGLISH.

49:43.714 --> 49:46.151
IS VERY BEAUTIFUL,
YOUR CAR.

49:46.217 --> 49:50.155
GOOD NIGHT, ENRIQUE.
BUENAS NOCHES, SENORA.

49:50.221 --> 49:52.323
[ Engine Starts ]

50:05.870 --> 50:08.139
[ Traffic Passing ]

50:08.206 --> 50:11.909
* SINCE I MET YOU, BABY *

50:11.976 --> 50:16.481
* MY WHOLE LIFE
HAS CHANGED *

50:16.547 --> 50:19.150
* [ Continues ]

50:21.119 --> 50:24.722
* SINCE I MET YOU, BABY *

50:24.789 --> 50:27.825
* MY WHOLE LIFE
HAS CHANGED *
CAROLYN.

50:27.892 --> 50:30.061
KNOCK THAT OFF A MINUTE.

50:34.299 --> 50:37.034
* AND IF-- *

50:41.772 --> 50:47.178
- BLACK SEMINOLES ?
- HOBBY OF MINE.

50:47.245 --> 50:48.613
A FEW ARTIFACTS.

50:48.679 --> 50:52.850
COUPLE OF PIECES ONE OF YOUR MEN
OUT ON THE BASE MADE.

50:52.917 --> 50:54.919
ADMISSION'S FREE.

50:54.985 --> 50:56.821
AH.

50:59.990 --> 51:02.527
THIS IS WHERE HE WAS SHOT ?

51:02.593 --> 51:05.029
HE FELL RIGHT THERE
BY THE DOOR.

51:05.096 --> 51:07.398
GET MUCH OF THAT IN HERE ?

51:08.599 --> 51:13.070
IT'S A BAR.
FOLKS COME TOGETHER.

51:13.138 --> 51:18.443
DRINK, FALL IN LOVE,
FALL OUTTA LOVE,
AIR THEIR GRUDGES OUT.

51:18.509 --> 51:21.246
DEAL DRUGS IN THE BATHROOM.

51:21.312 --> 51:26.784
IF I THOUGHT IT WOULD DO
ANY GOOD, I'D PUT UP A SIGN
TELLIN' 'EM NOT TO.

51:26.851 --> 51:30.988
RIGHT NEXT TO THE ONE
ABOUT THE EMPLOYEES
WASHIN' THEIR HANDS.

51:31.055 --> 51:34.425
THIS HERE IS CAROLYN.

51:34.492 --> 51:38.629
HONEY, THIS IS MY SON,
DELMORE.

51:40.831 --> 51:42.700
NICE TO MEET YOU, MA'AM.

51:44.735 --> 51:48.673
I'LL BE IN BACK,
WAITING FOR THAT DELIVERY.

51:51.942 --> 51:54.812
[ Door Opens ]

51:54.879 --> 51:56.981
[ Door Closes ]
SO ?

51:57.047 --> 51:58.449
SO.

52:00.818 --> 52:04.189
TELL ME WHY I SHOULDN'T
MAKE THIS PLACE OFF-LIMITS.

52:06.524 --> 52:08.826
THIS IS AN
OFFICIAL VISIT THEN.

52:08.893 --> 52:12.863
I ASSUME MOST OF YOUR BUSINESS
IS WITH OUR PEOPLE.

52:14.465 --> 52:17.268
YOUR BOYS ALL COOPED UP
TOGETHER OUT THERE.

52:17.335 --> 52:19.470
THEY NEED SOMEPLACE
TO LET THE STEAM OUT.

52:19.537 --> 52:25.876
IF THEY BLACK, THERE'S NOT
BUT ONE SPOT IN THIS COUNTY
WHERE THEY FEEL WELCOME.

52:25.943 --> 52:29.747
IT'S BEEN THAT WAY
SINCE BEFORE YOU WERE BORN.

52:29.814 --> 52:33.784
WE HAVE AN ENLISTED MEN'S CLUB
AT THE POST.

52:33.851 --> 52:38.856
YOU THE MAN OUT THERE NOW,
AIN'T YA ? IT'S YOUR CALL.

52:38.923 --> 52:40.558
THAT'S RIGHT.

52:43.093 --> 52:49.133
I'VE BEEN HEARING ABOUT
THIS NEW COMMANDER OUT THERE
FOR A COUPLE OF WEEKS NOW.

52:49.200 --> 52:52.437
BOYS SAY THEY HEAR
HE'S A HARD CASE.

52:52.503 --> 52:54.739
A REAL SPIT AND POLISH MAN.

52:54.805 --> 52:59.009
FULL BIRD COLONEL
BY THE NAME OF PAYNE.

52:59.076 --> 53:01.579
BET YOU NEVER FIGURED
YOU'D END UP BACK HERE.

53:03.781 --> 53:08.185
THE ARMY OFFERS YOU A COMMAND,
YOU GO WHEREVER IT IS.

53:09.186 --> 53:10.988
RIGHT.

53:11.055 --> 53:17.895
I HEAR THINGS TOO.
THEY CALL YOU
THE MAYOR OF DARKTOWN.

53:17.962 --> 53:22.633
OVER THE YEARS,
THIS IS THE ONE PLACE
THAT'S ALWAYS BEEN THERE.

53:22.700 --> 53:26.337
I LOAN A LITTLE MONEY OUT.
I SETTLE A FEW ARGUMENTS.

53:26.404 --> 53:31.976
I GOT A COT IN THE BACK.
FOLKS GET SCARED TO GO HOME,
THEY CAN SPEND THE NIGHT.

53:32.042 --> 53:35.946
THERE'S NOT ENOUGH OF US TO
RUN ANYTHING IN THIS TOWN.

53:37.982 --> 53:42.287
IT'S HOLINESS CHURCH
OR BIG O'S.

53:44.188 --> 53:45.990
AND THE PEOPLE
MAKE A CHOICE.

53:47.525 --> 53:50.227
MOST OF 'EM CHOOSE BOTH.

53:50.295 --> 53:52.797
THERE'S NOT LIKE
THERE'S A BORDERLINE...

53:52.863 --> 53:56.534
BETWEEN THE GOOD PEOPLE
AND THE BAD PEOPLE.

53:56.601 --> 53:59.270
YOU'RE NOT ON EITHER
ONE SIDE OR THE OTHER.

54:02.973 --> 54:04.275
RIGHT.

54:06.577 --> 54:08.313
I'M GONNA MEET
THAT FAMILY OF YOURS ?

54:12.517 --> 54:15.052
WHY WOULD YOU
WANT TO DO THAT ?

54:15.119 --> 54:18.289
BECAUSE... I'M YOUR FATHER.

54:25.763 --> 54:29.266
YOU'LL GET
OFFICIAL NOTIFICATION
WHEN I MAKE MY DECISION.

54:41.145 --> 54:42.713
[ Door Slams ]

54:46.517 --> 54:49.620
SO THAT'S HIM.
YEAH, THAT'S HIM.

54:51.188 --> 54:53.591
HISTORIC OCCASION,
AIN'T IT ?

54:53.658 --> 54:55.993
YEAH, SEEMS LIKE WE HAVE
ANOTHER ONE EVERY WEEK.

54:56.060 --> 54:59.930
JORGE AND THE BOYS
AT THE CHAMBER OF COMMERCE
GOTTA KEEP THINGS HUMMIN'.

54:59.997 --> 55:03.734
BUILDIN' UP TOURISM, SAM.
PEOPLE COME
HERE TO CATCH BASS...

55:03.801 --> 55:06.971
AND TO GET LAID AT
THE BOY'S TOWN IN CIUDAD LEON.

55:07.037 --> 55:11.409
YOU OUGHT TO PUT UP A BANNER:
"FRONTERA, TEXAS, GATEWAY
TO INEXPENSIVE PUSSY."

55:11.476 --> 55:14.479
THAT KIND OF TALK
DON'T HELP.

55:14.545 --> 55:17.748
I'D RATHER HAVE THAT
THAN THE TEN-FOOT-HIGH
CATFISH STATUTE.

55:17.815 --> 55:21.719
I GOT EDDIE RICHTER
AT THE SENTINEL TO KILL
THAT STORY, SAM.

55:21.786 --> 55:26.424
WHAT, THE PERDIDO THING ?
HE AGREED IT
WASN'T EXACTLY NEWS.

55:26.491 --> 55:28.893
DANNY'S GONNA BE OUT
FOR BLOOD THE NEXT TIME.

55:28.959 --> 55:31.796
THAT'S THE REASON
WE WANTED TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT THE NEW JAIL.

55:31.862 --> 55:34.699
JUST SO'S WE'RE
ON THE SAME PAGE.
WE DON'T NEED A NEW JAIL.

55:34.765 --> 55:38.803
THAT'S A MATTER OF OPINION.
WE'RE ALREADY RENTIN' CELLS
TO THE FEDS FOR OVERFLOW.

55:38.869 --> 55:41.305
THERE WAS A MANDATE
IN THE LAST ELECTION--
IT WOULDN'T HAPPEN TO BE...

55:41.372 --> 55:46.444
YOUR CONSTRUCTION COMPANY
GONNA GET THE BID ON BUILDIN'
THIS THING, WOULD IT, FENTON ?

55:46.511 --> 55:51.916
AND JORGE,
YOU WOULDN'T BE THINKIN' ABOUT
A COUPLE DOZEN NEW JOBS...

55:51.982 --> 55:55.586
TO DANGLE IN FRONT
OF THE VOTERS WHEN YOU RUN
FOR MAYOR NEXT ELECTION ?

55:55.653 --> 55:59.323
THE PEOPLE ARE
CONCERNED ABOUT CRIME.

55:59.390 --> 56:02.560
I'M NOT GONNA CAMPAIGN
AGAINST YOUR DEAL HERE.

56:02.627 --> 56:05.329
BUT IF ANYBODY ASKS ME,
I GOT TO TELL THEM THE TRUTH.

56:05.396 --> 56:07.898
WE DON'T NEED A NEW JAIL.

56:07.965 --> 56:10.267
- WHEN WE BACKED YOU--
- WHEN YOU BACKED ME,

56:10.334 --> 56:13.938
YOU NEEDED SOMEBODY NAMED DEEDS
TO BUMP THE OTHER FELLOW
OUTTA OFFICE.

56:16.574 --> 56:18.275
[ Woman ]
HI, SAM.
HEY, FOLKS.

56:18.342 --> 56:21.612
[ Man ]
FENTON, WHAT'S UP, BUDDY ?
HI ! HOW YOU DOIN' ?

56:21.679 --> 56:23.614
LET'S GET THIS THING
OVER WITH.
GOOD TO SEE YA.

56:29.386 --> 56:32.022
[ Bullet Casings Rattling ]

56:34.525 --> 56:38.295
I NEVER THOUGHT I'D SEE
THE DAY A BUDDY OF MINE
WOULD BE DATIN' A WOMAN...

56:38.362 --> 56:40.765
WITH THREE BARS
ON HER SHOULDER.

56:40.831 --> 56:42.800
IT'S BEYOND
WHAT YOU'D CALL DATING.

56:42.867 --> 56:46.036
YOU GONNA GET MARRIED ?
MAYBE.

56:46.103 --> 56:48.138
YOU MET HER FAMILY ?

56:48.205 --> 56:50.741
THEY GONNA BE
COOL ABOUT YOU
BEIN' A WHITE GUY ?

56:50.808 --> 56:56.213
PRISCILLA SAYS THEY THINK
ANY WOMAN OVER 30 WHO'S NOT
MARRIED MUST BE A LESBIAN.

56:56.280 --> 56:58.783
SHE FIGURES
THEY'LL BE SO RELIEVED
THAT I'M A MAN--

56:58.849 --> 57:03.420
IT'S ALWAYS HEARTWARMING
TO SEE A PREJUDICE DEFEATED
BY A DEEPER PREJUDICE.

57:03.488 --> 57:06.924
MARRIAGE, MAN.
I DON'T KNOW.

57:06.991 --> 57:11.462
LET'S SEE. I DID TWO TOURS
OF DUTY IN SOUTHEAST ASIA.

57:11.529 --> 57:14.031
I WAS MARRIED
FOR FIVE YEARS.

57:14.098 --> 57:17.167
I COULDN'T TELL YOU
WHICH EXPERIENCE WAS WORSE.
HEY, MIKEY.

57:17.234 --> 57:21.405
I KNEW SHE WAS JAPANESE
GOIN' INTO IT, BUT SHE DIDN'T
TELL ME THE NINJA ASSASSIN PART.

57:21.472 --> 57:23.173
MIKEY.
HER PARENTS
ACTED LIKE...

57:23.240 --> 57:25.209
I WAS GONNA BLOW MY NOSE
ON THEIR CURTAINS.

57:25.275 --> 57:28.078
MIKEY.
IF I STAYED OUT
PAST 10:00 WITH THE GUYS,

57:28.145 --> 57:30.447
SHE'D GO INTO THIS
MADAME BUTTERFLY ROUTINE.

57:30.515 --> 57:32.349
HEY, MIKEY.
LOOK AT THIS.

57:32.416 --> 57:36.220
WHAT ? IT'S A BULLET.
I'M LOUSY WITH BULLETS HERE.

57:36.286 --> 57:38.689
- IT'S A .45.
- OH, YEAH ?

57:38.756 --> 57:41.559
THIS IS THE STUFF
WE PICKED UP
THE OTHER DAY, RIGHT ?

57:41.626 --> 57:43.761
THE REST OF THIS
IS ALL .30 CALIBER.

57:43.828 --> 57:46.597
THEY WERE
USING M-1'S, YEAH.
YEAH.

57:46.664 --> 57:51.602
SO WHAT'S A PISTOL SLUG
DOIN' ON A RIFLE RANGE ?

57:51.669 --> 57:53.170
WE BETTER CALL
THAT SHERIFF.

57:55.439 --> 57:58.108
BACK IN THE EARLY '70s,

57:58.175 --> 58:03.480
A REPORTER FROM A NATIONAL
MAGAZINE ASKED THE GOVERNOR
OF OUR LONE STAR STATE,

58:03.548 --> 58:06.617
"GOVERNOR,
WHAT'S YOUR IDEAL...

58:06.684 --> 58:10.521
OF WHAT A REAL TEXAN
OUGHTA BE ?"

58:10.588 --> 58:14.024
GOVERNOR SAID,
"SON, THAT'S EASY.

58:14.091 --> 58:17.762
"JUST GO DOWN TO RIO COUNTY
AND GET A LOOK...

58:17.828 --> 58:20.531
AT SHERIFF BUDDY DEEDS."

58:20.598 --> 58:24.101
[ Applause ]
THANK YOU.

58:24.168 --> 58:29.006
THERE'S, UH, ONE MORE PERSON
WE OUGHT TO HEAR FROM.

58:29.073 --> 58:33.678
I THINK HE'S SOMEBODY WHO KNEW
BUDDY BETTER THAN ANY OF US.

58:33.744 --> 58:36.681
SAM, UH, SAY A FEW WORDS ?

58:36.747 --> 58:39.717
[ Applause ]

58:41.752 --> 58:45.556
WELL, YOU FOLKS
WHO REMEMBER MY FATHER...

58:45.623 --> 58:47.725
KNEW HIM AS SHERIFF.

58:47.792 --> 58:53.731
BUT AT HOME, HE WAS ALSO
JUDGE, JURY AND EXECUTIONER.

58:53.798 --> 58:56.567
[ Scattered Laughter ]

58:56.634 --> 59:00.104
THIS IS A REAL HONOR
YOU'RE DOIN' HIM TODAY.

59:00.170 --> 59:02.640
AND IF BUDDY WAS AROUND,
I'M SURE HIS HAT SIZE...

59:02.707 --> 59:06.844
WOULD BE GETTIN'
A LOT BIGGER EVERY MINUTE.

59:06.911 --> 59:09.914
I USED TO THINK THERE
WASN'T A PLACE IN THIS TOWN...

59:09.980 --> 59:13.350
YOU COULD HIDE
FROM MY OLD MAN.

59:13.417 --> 59:15.319
AND NOW I'M SURE OF IT.

59:15.385 --> 59:17.688
[ Scattered Laughter ]

59:17.755 --> 59:20.524
I DO APPRECIATE IT THOUGH.

59:20.591 --> 59:24.795
AND WHEREVER HE IS,
BUDDY'S PUTTIN' THE BEER
ON ICE FOR THE BUNCH OF YA.

59:24.862 --> 59:27.297
THANK YOU.
[ Applause ]

59:29.667 --> 59:33.170
AND NOW MY FAVORITE
COUNCIL MEMBER...

59:33.237 --> 59:37.808
AND ONE OF FRONTERA'S
MOST RESPECTED BUSINESSWOMEN,

59:37.875 --> 59:42.012
MRS. MERCEDES CRUZ,
WILL DO THE HONORS.

59:42.079 --> 59:44.649
[ Applause ]

59:46.383 --> 59:49.687
[ Man ]
SENORA CRUZ, ESPERA
UN MOMENTO. COMO ESTO.

59:49.754 --> 59:52.122
[ Camera Shutter Clicks ]
GRACIAS.

59:54.024 --> 59:55.860
[ Applause ]

01:00:00.297 --> 01:00:02.499
[ Jorge ]
IT DOES LOOK
KIND OF LIKE BUDDY.

01:00:02.566 --> 01:00:05.670
[ Fenton ]
I THINK HE'S GONNA RUN THAT
MEXICAN KID IN FOR LOITERING.

01:00:05.736 --> 01:00:07.638
NICE TO SEE YOU, MRS. CRUZ.

01:00:12.042 --> 01:00:16.380
[ Danny Chattering,
Indistinct ]

01:00:19.416 --> 01:00:22.519
FIELD TRIP ?
LUNCH HOUR.

01:00:22.586 --> 01:00:27.257
MY NEXT CLASS
ISN'T UNTIL 1:30.

01:00:27.324 --> 01:00:29.960
YOU WANT
TO TAKE A WALK ?

01:00:41.538 --> 01:00:45.209
THEY COOKED
THE WHOLE THING UP
WITHOUT ASKING ME.

01:00:45.275 --> 01:00:46.811
PEOPLE LIKED HIM.

01:00:48.879 --> 01:00:52.049
MOST PEOPLE DID.
YEAH.

01:00:53.951 --> 01:00:56.887
I REMEMBER HIM
WATCHING ME ONCE...

01:00:56.954 --> 01:00:59.156
WHEN I WAS LITTLE...

01:00:59.223 --> 01:01:00.991
BEFORE YOU AND I--

01:01:03.961 --> 01:01:07.164
I WAS ON THE PLAYGROUND
WITH ALL THE OTHER KIDS.

01:01:07.231 --> 01:01:11.101
BUT I THOUGHT
HE WAS ONLY LOOKING AT ME.

01:01:11.168 --> 01:01:14.138
I WAS AFRAID
HE WAS GONNA ARREST ME.

01:01:14.204 --> 01:01:17.975
HE HAD THOSE EYES,
YOU KNOW, AND THAT--
YEAH.

01:01:18.042 --> 01:01:22.346
HMM. IT'S WEIRD
WHAT YOU REMEMBER.

01:01:27.051 --> 01:01:29.987
- HEY, YOUR BOY THERE--
- AMADO.

01:01:30.054 --> 01:01:32.622
- NICE-LOOKIN' KID.
- HE HATES ME.

01:01:32.689 --> 01:01:36.460
[ Chuckles ]
NO.

01:01:36.526 --> 01:01:40.030
WITH PALOMA, IT'S MORE LIKE
SHE PITIES AND TOLERATES ME.

01:01:40.097 --> 01:01:41.766
TOTALLY AGE APPROPRIATE.

01:01:41.832 --> 01:01:47.137
BUT WITH AMADO--
HE'S ALWAYS HAD
DIFFICULTY READING.

01:01:47.204 --> 01:01:50.607
AND ME BEING
A TEACHER AND CARING
ABOUT THOSE THINGS,

01:01:50.674 --> 01:01:53.543
IT'S LIKE... A BETRAYAL.

01:01:53.610 --> 01:01:56.947
FERNANDO DID OKAY.
HE DROPPED OUT.

01:01:57.014 --> 01:01:58.749
FERNANDO WASN'T
PISSED OFF AT EVERYBODY.

01:01:58.816 --> 01:02:03.153
HE JUST WANTED
TO FIX THEIR CARS.

01:02:03.220 --> 01:02:07.524
I SPENT MY FIRST
15 YEARS TRYIN' TO BE
JUST LIKE BUDDY.

01:02:07.591 --> 01:02:11.061
NEXT FIFTEEN TRYIN'
TO GIVE HIM A HEART ATTACK.

01:02:13.798 --> 01:02:15.900
[ Sighs ]

01:02:18.168 --> 01:02:22.472
SO WHY DID YOU
COME BACK HERE, SAM ?

01:02:24.441 --> 01:02:25.776
I GOT DIVORCED.

01:02:29.079 --> 01:02:32.983
I WASN'T GONNA WORK FOR
MY FATHER-IN-LAW ANYMORE.

01:02:33.050 --> 01:02:37.822
THE FELLAS DOWN HERE,
THEY SAID THEY'D BACK ME.

01:02:39.756 --> 01:02:41.691
YOU DON'T WANNA BE SHERIFF.

01:02:41.758 --> 01:02:47.064
[ Chuckles ]
I GOTTA ADMIT, IT'S NOT
WHAT I THOUGHT IT'D BE.

01:02:47.131 --> 01:02:50.868
BACK WHEN BUDDY HAD IT--

01:02:53.804 --> 01:02:57.307
HELL, I'M JUST A JAILER.

01:02:57.374 --> 01:03:02.346
I RUN A 60-ROOM HOTEL
WITH BARS ON THE WINDOWS.

01:03:05.349 --> 01:03:07.952
YOU REMEMBER THIS ?

01:03:09.086 --> 01:03:12.990
I, UM--
I OUGHTA HEAD BACK.

01:03:13.057 --> 01:03:17.361
PILAR--
IT LOOKS REAL BAD
IF THE TEACHER'S
LATE FOR CLASS.

01:03:19.363 --> 01:03:23.267
IT'S REAL NICE
TO TALK WITH YOU, SAM.

01:03:52.262 --> 01:03:53.998
[ Boy ]
ARE YOU GONNA TELL HER ?

01:03:56.500 --> 01:03:57.902
YOU GONNA TELL HIM ?

01:03:57.968 --> 01:04:00.104
HE DOESN'T NEED TO KNOW
ALL MY BUSINESS.

01:04:00.170 --> 01:04:02.172
HE'S GONNA FIND OUT.

01:04:02.239 --> 01:04:05.275
SO ? WHAT'S HE GONNA DO ?
ARREST US ?

01:04:07.711 --> 01:04:12.116
IT'S SUPPOSED
TO BE SOME BIG SIN EVEN
IF YOU LOVE EACH OTHER.

01:04:12.182 --> 01:04:14.351
YOU BELIEVE THAT ?

01:04:16.586 --> 01:04:18.422
NO.

01:04:33.870 --> 01:04:35.105
ME NEITHER.

01:04:38.142 --> 01:04:39.609
[ Worth ]
PRIVATE JOHNSON !

01:04:42.379 --> 01:04:46.616
REPORT TO SERGEANT BURR IN THE
ORDERLY'S ROOM. THE DOCTOR'S
GONNA HAVE A LOOK AT YOU.

01:04:46.683 --> 01:04:47.985
I'M FEELIN' OKAY.

01:04:48.052 --> 01:04:50.054
I'M REAL HAPPY
TO HEAR THAT, PRIVATE.

01:04:50.120 --> 01:04:55.092
GO PUT SOME PEE-PEE
IN A CUP FOR DR. INNIS, AND
I'M GONNA BE FEELIN' OKAY TOO.

01:04:55.159 --> 01:04:57.027
Y-YOU TESTIN' ME ?

01:04:57.094 --> 01:05:02.566
YOU AND 119 OTHER
FORTUNATE INDIVIDUALS.
PUT IT IN GEAR.

01:05:06.670 --> 01:05:08.705
TAKE THIS SHIT OFF NOW.
YOU BEEN TALKIN'
SO MUCH TRASH TODAY,

01:05:08.772 --> 01:05:10.807
YOU GOT US THINKIN'
YOU'RE A DANGEROUS CRIMINAL.

01:05:10.874 --> 01:05:13.677
YOU BETTER BE GOOD, BOY.
"BOY" ? YOU'RE THE ONE
WHO'S A GOOD BOY.

01:05:13.743 --> 01:05:16.680
MAN SAY FETCH
AND YOU FETCH.
JUST DOIN' MY JOB.

01:05:16.746 --> 01:05:19.183
WHITE MAN JUST USIN' YOU
TO KEEP THE BLACK MAN DOWN.

01:05:19.249 --> 01:05:23.387
THIS ISN'T HOUSTON, FRIEND.
WE'RE RUNNING THINGS NOW.
OUR GOOD DAY HAS COME.

01:05:23.453 --> 01:05:26.090
YOU CHUMPS
AIN'T HAD A GOOD DAY
SINCE THE ALAMO.

01:05:26.156 --> 01:05:27.691
ANDALE, AMIGO.

01:05:33.597 --> 01:05:39.003
LUPE ? WOULD YOU GET ME
BEN WETZEL UP IN AUSTIN ?

01:05:42.139 --> 01:05:45.976
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

01:05:49.713 --> 01:05:51.648
[ Sighs ]

01:05:53.017 --> 01:05:56.086
* [ Continues ]

01:06:04.294 --> 01:06:07.231
[ Man Whispering ]
i VAMONOS !

01:06:13.803 --> 01:06:16.140
WETBACKS AGAIN.

01:06:17.774 --> 01:06:20.277
[ Beeps ]

01:06:22.079 --> 01:06:26.450
HELLO ? BORDER PATROL ?

01:06:26.516 --> 01:06:28.718
* [ Guitar ]

01:06:28.785 --> 01:06:33.690
[ Chattering ]

01:06:33.757 --> 01:06:37.161
* [ Singing In Spanish ]

01:06:48.905 --> 01:06:51.841
[ Diners Laughing ]

01:06:51.908 --> 01:06:55.179
* [ Continues ]

01:07:07.091 --> 01:07:10.427
* [ Continues
In Distance ]

01:07:22.872 --> 01:07:25.542
[ Footfalls Approaching ]

01:07:27.344 --> 01:07:29.613
MOM ?
YEAH ?

01:07:29.679 --> 01:07:34.284
YOU GONNA
STAY OUT HERE ?
YEAH. FOR A WHILE.

01:07:36.353 --> 01:07:41.057
WHAT'S SHE
SINGIN' ABOUT ?
WHAT DO YOU THINK ?

01:09:15.185 --> 01:09:16.653
[ Door Opens ]

01:09:18.354 --> 01:09:20.457
HEY !
GOOD MORNING, SHERIFF !

01:09:20.524 --> 01:09:24.461
- HEY, PETE. HOW'S IT GOIN' ?
- TIME MARCHES ON.

01:09:24.528 --> 01:09:28.798
- HOW MUCH YOU GOT LEFT ?
- THREE MONTHS.

01:09:28.865 --> 01:09:32.702
STOP GROWIN' THAT LOCOWEED
AT YOUR PLACE, YOU'D SEE
A LOT MORE DAYLIGHT.

01:09:32.769 --> 01:09:35.572
IT WAS FOR
PERSONAL CONSUMPTION.

01:09:35.639 --> 01:09:39.309
YOU GONNA SMOKE
AN ACRE AND A HALF
OF MARIJUANA ?

01:09:39.376 --> 01:09:42.546
LOOK, I GOT A BAD STOMACH.
IT HELPS ME TO DIGEST.

01:09:42.612 --> 01:09:44.948
YOUR FATHER NEVER
BOTHERED ME ABOUT IT.

01:09:45.014 --> 01:09:50.254
LEASTWAYS, NOT 'TIL THOSE
DRUG PEOPLE GOT ON HIS CASE
IN THE LATE '60s.

01:09:50.319 --> 01:09:53.122
I THOUGHT HE BUSTED YA
A COUPLE OF TIMES.

01:09:53.189 --> 01:09:56.660
NO. DIFFERENT CHARGE.

01:09:56.726 --> 01:09:58.428
I HAD A STILL.

01:09:58.495 --> 01:10:01.865
I MADE MY OWN MESCAL. THAT'S
HOW COME I RUINED MY STOMACH.

01:10:01.931 --> 01:10:04.634
I'M SURPRISED
HE BOTHERED WITH IT.

01:10:04.701 --> 01:10:09.138
HE WAS AFRAID I WAS GOING
TO POISON SOMEBODY.

01:10:09.205 --> 01:10:12.742
- YOUR FATHER TRIED
TO DO GOOD FOR PEOPLE.
- SO I HEARD.

01:10:12.809 --> 01:10:15.845
AND YOUR MOTHER,
SHE WAS A SAINT.

01:10:15.912 --> 01:10:18.715
YOU REMEMBER THAT SUMMER
WHEN I BUILT THAT PATIO
AT YOUR HOUSE ?

01:10:18.782 --> 01:10:21.818
SHE MADE ME LUNCH
EVERY DAY.

01:10:21.885 --> 01:10:23.620
YOU WERE WORKIN' THERE.

01:10:23.687 --> 01:10:26.856
IT COULD HAVE BEEN JUST
ANOTHER BOX LUNCH FROM THE JAIL.

01:10:26.923 --> 01:10:30.827
YOU BUILT OUR PATIO
WHILE YOU WERE ON THE COUNTY ?

01:10:30.894 --> 01:10:34.631
OUT IN THE FRESH AIR,
NICE GRINGA LADY
MAKIN' YOU PIES.

01:10:34.698 --> 01:10:37.467
WHO THE HELL'S GONNA SIT BACK
IN A LITTLE JAIL CELL ALL DAY ?

01:10:37.534 --> 01:10:40.604
[ Laughs ]
OH, SHERIFF BUDDY, MAN.

01:10:40.670 --> 01:10:42.872
COMO EL NO HAY DOS.

01:10:42.939 --> 01:10:44.674
AND AFTER
THAT CABRON CHARLIE WADE.

01:10:44.741 --> 01:10:48.445
I HEARD WADE WAS A BIT TOUGH
ON THE MEXICANS.

01:10:52.882 --> 01:10:56.853
HE MURDERED ELADIO CRUZ.
IS THAT TOUGH ENOUGH FOR YOU ?

01:10:58.788 --> 01:10:59.856
MURDERED HIM ?

01:10:59.923 --> 01:11:03.460
CHUCHO MONTOYA SAW IT
WITH HIS OWN EYES.

01:11:03.527 --> 01:11:06.330
[ Imitates Gunshot ]
SHOT HIM IN COLD BLOOD.

01:11:06.396 --> 01:11:09.866
ERA MUY CABRON
ESE CHARLIE WADE.

01:11:09.933 --> 01:11:10.967
SAM !

01:11:13.770 --> 01:11:15.372
UH, SAM, WAIT UP.

01:11:19.976 --> 01:11:21.077
YOU'RE OUT EARLY.

01:11:21.144 --> 01:11:22.412
YEAH.

01:11:22.479 --> 01:11:25.649
HAVEN'T SEEN MUCH OF YOU
AT THE JAIL LATELY.

01:11:25.715 --> 01:11:28.352
I'M WORKIN' ON
A FEW THINGS.
UH-HUH.

01:11:28.418 --> 01:11:32.055
I'M GOIN' OVER
TO THE OTHER SIDE.

01:11:32.121 --> 01:11:35.191
THE REPUBLICANS ?
NO. MEXICO.

01:11:35.258 --> 01:11:37.527
OH.
GOTTA TALK TO SOMEONE.

01:11:37.594 --> 01:11:40.296
WELL, THEY GOT TELEPHONES.

01:11:40.364 --> 01:11:42.999
NO. IT'S GOTTA
BE IN PERSON.

01:11:46.135 --> 01:11:50.306
SAM, I--
I, UH--

01:11:50.374 --> 01:11:53.710
THE COMMITTEE--
JORGE AND FENTON AND ALL--

01:11:53.777 --> 01:11:56.613
THEY, UH--
WELL, THEY'VE ASKED ME IF--

01:11:56.680 --> 01:12:00.717
THEY WANT YOU TO STAND
FOR SHERIFF NEXT ELECTION.

01:12:00.784 --> 01:12:02.419
YEAH.

01:12:03.420 --> 01:12:05.422
YOU'D DO A GOOD JOB.

01:12:07.123 --> 01:12:10.560
THANKS.
WHAT ABOUT YOU ?

01:12:10.627 --> 01:12:13.329
I DON'T KNOW
IF I'LL STILL WANT IT.

01:12:15.198 --> 01:12:19.202
I, UH, JUST DIDN'T WANT
TO GO AROUND YOUR BACK.
THAT'S ALL.

01:12:19.268 --> 01:12:21.104
APPRECIATE YOU TELLIN' ME.

01:12:24.708 --> 01:12:26.576
YOU THINK WE NEED
A NEW JAIL ?

01:12:29.813 --> 01:12:34.451
WELL, SAM, UM,
IT'S A COMPLICATED ISSUE.

01:12:37.020 --> 01:12:38.955
YEAH. RIGHT.

01:12:39.022 --> 01:12:42.559
YOU'D BE A HELL
OF A SHERIFF.

01:12:42.626 --> 01:12:44.127
[ Car Engine Starts ]

01:12:46.396 --> 01:12:50.299
* [ Spanish ]

01:12:50.366 --> 01:12:54.904
[ Men On Radio
Hawking In Spanish ]

01:12:58.207 --> 01:13:01.578
[ Men Continue ]

01:13:11.488 --> 01:13:16.460
[ Men Continue ]

01:13:28.872 --> 01:13:31.040
[ Radio Fades ]

01:13:34.578 --> 01:13:39.849
[ Man ] DOWN HERE
WE DON'T THROW EVERYTHING AWAY
LIKE YOU GRINGOS DO.

01:13:40.984 --> 01:13:42.552
RECYCLING, RIGHT ?

01:13:44.420 --> 01:13:46.355
WE INVENTED THAT.

01:13:46.422 --> 01:13:50.594
THE GOVERNMENT DOESN'T HAVE
TO TELL PEOPLE TO DO IT.

01:13:51.928 --> 01:13:55.765
SO YOU OWN THIS PLACE,
HUH ?

01:13:55.832 --> 01:14:00.637
THIS PLACE, THE ONE
ACROSS THE STREET.

01:14:00.704 --> 01:14:04.273
THREE OR FOUR OTHERS
IN CIUDAD LEON.

01:14:04.340 --> 01:14:07.877
SOY EL REY DE LAS LLANTAS.

01:14:07.944 --> 01:14:09.546
KING OF THE TIRES.

01:14:11.781 --> 01:14:16.152
A LOT OF YOUR PEOPLE
ROLLING OVER THAT BRIDGE
ON MY RUBBER.

01:14:16.219 --> 01:14:19.222
YOU LIVED IN THE STATES
FOR A WHILE ?

01:14:19.288 --> 01:14:21.290
FIFTEEN YEARS.

01:14:21.357 --> 01:14:24.661
MADE SOME MONEY,
CAME BACK HERE.

01:14:24.728 --> 01:14:27.030
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

01:14:27.096 --> 01:14:31.034
YOU EVER KNOW A FELLOW
NAMED ELADIO CRUZ ?

01:14:33.737 --> 01:14:36.405
YOU'RE THE SHERIFF
OF RIO COUNTY, RIGHT ?

01:14:36.472 --> 01:14:38.742
UN JEFE MUY RESPETADO.

01:14:51.120 --> 01:14:53.056
STEP ACROSS THIS LINE.

01:14:55.825 --> 01:14:58.528
i AY, QUE MILAGRO !

01:14:59.863 --> 01:15:03.366
YOU'RE NOT THE SHERIFF
OF NOTHING ANYMORE.

01:15:03.432 --> 01:15:07.503
JUST SOME TEJANO
WITH A LOT OF QUESTIONS
I DON'T HAVE TO ANSWER.

01:15:09.105 --> 01:15:11.374
A BIRD FLYING SOUTH.

01:15:11.440 --> 01:15:14.143
YOU THINK HE SEES THIS LINE ?

01:15:14.210 --> 01:15:17.380
RATTLESNAKE, JAVELINA,

01:15:17.446 --> 01:15:19.448
WHATEVER YOU GOT.

01:15:19.515 --> 01:15:23.653
YOU THINK HALFWAY ACROSS
THAT LINE THEY START
THINKING DIFFERENT ?

01:15:23.720 --> 01:15:26.189
WHY SHOULD A MAN ?

01:15:26.255 --> 01:15:30.594
YOUR GOVERNMENT'S
ALWAYS BEEN PRETTY HAPPY
TO HAVE THAT LINE.

01:15:30.660 --> 01:15:32.662
THE QUESTION'S JUST BEEN
WHERE TO DRAW IT.

01:15:38.134 --> 01:15:43.072
MY GOVERNMENT
CAN GO FUCK ITSELF
AND SO CAN YOURS.

01:15:43.139 --> 01:15:45.474
I'M TALKING
ABOUT PEOPLE HERE.

01:15:45.541 --> 01:15:47.611
MEN.

01:15:50.446 --> 01:15:54.984
MI AMIGO ELADIO CRUZ...

01:15:55.051 --> 01:15:59.122
WAS GIVING SOME FRIENDS
OF HIS A LIFT ONE DAY
IN THE BACK OF HIS CAMION.

01:15:59.188 --> 01:16:02.926
BUT BECAUSE THEY'RE ON ONE
SIDE OF THIS INVISIBLE LINE
AND NOT THE OTHER,

01:16:02.992 --> 01:16:06.095
THEY GOT TO HIDE IN
THE BACK COMO CRIMINALES.

01:16:06.162 --> 01:16:09.899
AND BECAUSE OVER THERE HE'S
JUST ANOTHER MEX BRACERO,

01:16:09.966 --> 01:16:12.035
ANY MAN WITH A BADGE
IS HIS JEFE.

01:16:12.101 --> 01:16:14.971
* [ Singing In Spanish
On Radio ]

01:16:25.882 --> 01:16:29.118
* [ Continues ]

01:16:30.954 --> 01:16:34.824
[ Car Approaching ]

01:17:01.517 --> 01:17:03.552
[ Car Door Closes ]

01:17:03.619 --> 01:17:07.757
* [ Continues ]

01:17:22.739 --> 01:17:24.841
[ Radio Off ]
WHAT'S IN THE BACK ?

01:17:24.908 --> 01:17:27.643
NOT MUCH, JEFE.
SOME WATERMELONS.

01:17:27.711 --> 01:17:31.981
DRIVIN' 'EM
UP FOR THE MARKET.
SHOULD BRING A GOOD PRICE.

01:17:35.618 --> 01:17:39.923
I HEARD SOMEBODY BEEN
HAULIN' WETS ON THIS ROAD.

01:17:39.989 --> 01:17:43.993
I HAVEN'T SEEN ANYBODY
DOING THAT.

01:17:44.060 --> 01:17:46.462
THIS SAME PERSON
BEEN BRAGGIN'
ALL OVER THE COUNTY...

01:17:46.529 --> 01:17:50.033
HOW HE DOESN'T HAVE TO CUT
THAT BIG GRINGO SHERIFF
IN ON IT.

01:17:50.099 --> 01:17:53.803
HE CAN RUN HIS OWN
OPERATION WITHOUT ANY HELP.

01:17:53.870 --> 01:17:56.139
Â¿ COMO SE LLAMA, AMIGO ?

01:17:56.205 --> 01:17:57.406
ELADIO CRUZ.

01:17:59.208 --> 01:18:02.779
YOU KNOW THIS ROAD'S
GOT A BAD REPUTATION,
ELADIO.

01:18:02.846 --> 01:18:06.983
- REPUTATION ?
- BANDIDOS, INJUNS.

01:18:07.050 --> 01:18:10.920
THERE'S MANY AN UNFORTUNATE
SOUL BEEN AMBUSHED
OUT ON THIS STRETCH.

01:18:10.987 --> 01:18:13.489
I HOPE YOU'RE CARRYIN'
SOME PROTECTION.

01:18:13.556 --> 01:18:15.992
PROTECTION ?

01:18:16.059 --> 01:18:21.130
YOU CARRYIN'
A FIREARM, SON ?
DON'T LIE TO ME NOW.

01:18:21.197 --> 01:18:25.468
SI. UN ESCOPETO.
JUST A SHOTGUN.

01:18:25.534 --> 01:18:27.236
JUST A SHOTGUN.

01:18:27.303 --> 01:18:31.707
BETTER LET ME
HAVE A LOOK AT THAT.

01:18:31.775 --> 01:18:33.810
[ Truck Door Creaks ]

01:18:39.348 --> 01:18:42.551
OH ! OH, JESUS !

01:18:42.618 --> 01:18:46.322
LITTLE GREASER
SON OF A BITCH IS RUNNIN'
A GODDAMN BUS SERVICE.

01:18:46.389 --> 01:18:49.325
THINK HE CAN MAKE A FOOL
OUT OF CHARLIE WADE.

01:18:49.392 --> 01:18:54.130
GET THEM WETS
OUT OF THE BACK, HOLLIS.
SEE WHAT WE'VE GOT.

01:18:57.100 --> 01:19:01.938
YOU KILLED HIM.
YOU GOT A TALENT FOR
STATIN' THE OBVIOUS, SON.

01:19:10.479 --> 01:19:13.482
[ Footfalls Approaching ]

01:19:33.402 --> 01:19:34.804
STEVE CALLED FOR YOU.

01:19:34.871 --> 01:19:38.641
STEVE ?
STEVE.
BOARD OF EDUCATION STEVE.

01:19:38.707 --> 01:19:44.447
WHO LIKES YOU.
HE GOES FOR US HOT-BLOODED
MEXICAN GIRLS. I CAN TELL.

01:19:44.513 --> 01:19:47.550
SPANISH, PLEASE.
MY MOTHER WOULD HAVE
A HEART ATTACK.

01:19:47.616 --> 01:19:49.285
YOUR MOTHER'S FAMILY
IS SPANISH ?

01:19:49.352 --> 01:19:51.420
SURE, THEY GO
BACK TO CORTEZ.

01:19:51.487 --> 01:19:55.825
WHEN HE WAS RIDING BY,
THEY WERE SQUATTING IN A HUT,
COOKING HAMSTERS FOR DINNER.

01:19:55.892 --> 01:19:59.695
YOU'VE GOT TO BE INTERESTED
IN SOMEBODY, PILAR.
ALL YOU DO IS WORK.

01:19:59.762 --> 01:20:03.166
ALL MY MOTHER DOES IS WORK.
THAT'S HOW YOU GET
TO BE SPANISH.

01:20:03.232 --> 01:20:06.302
HOW ABOUT THIS SHERIFF ?
SHERIFF ?

01:20:06.369 --> 01:20:08.872
THE OLD HIGH SCHOOL
HEARTTHROB SHERIFF ?

01:20:08.938 --> 01:20:11.140
THOUGHT YOU WERE
CRAZY ABOUT EACH OTHER.

01:20:11.207 --> 01:20:14.377
HE'S AVAILABLE,
YOU'RE AVAILABLE.

01:20:14.443 --> 01:20:16.946
I'M UNMARRIED.
I'M NOT AVAILABLE.

01:20:17.013 --> 01:20:21.117
YOU TOLD ME ONE TIME
IT WAS TRUE LOVE.

01:20:22.952 --> 01:20:26.655
NOBODY STAYS IN LOVE
FOR 23 YEARS.

01:20:26.722 --> 01:20:29.425
* [ Dramatic ]

01:20:29.492 --> 01:20:31.360
[ Dog Barking ]

01:20:34.163 --> 01:20:35.831
[ Woman Panting ]
[ Woman ]
COME ON. GET UP !

01:20:35.899 --> 01:20:39.002
I CAN'T ! I CAN'T !
GET UP !

01:20:48.912 --> 01:20:51.847
[ Dog Barking ]

01:20:52.615 --> 01:20:55.518
[ Barking Continues ]

01:21:03.459 --> 01:21:05.161
[ Buddy ]
LET'S GO.

01:21:06.029 --> 01:21:09.966
GODDAMN IT !
COME HERE.

01:21:10.033 --> 01:21:12.768
WHAT THE HELL ARE YOU DOIN',
YOU ASSHOLE ?
HOW OLD IS THAT GIRL, HUH ?

01:21:12.835 --> 01:21:16.672
LET ME GO! i PENDEJO !
COME ON NOW, MISSY.
GET YOUR CLOTHES IN ORDER.

01:21:16.739 --> 01:21:19.742
HUH ? WHERE'S
YOUR GODDAMN SENSE, SON ?
YOU GOT NO FUCKIN' RIGHT.

01:21:19.808 --> 01:21:21.810
STAY OUTTA MY LIFE !

01:21:21.877 --> 01:21:25.181
GIVE ME THE GODDAMN CAR KEYS.
WHAT AM I SUPPOSED
TO DO WITH HER, BUDDY ?

01:21:25.248 --> 01:21:28.084
DRIVE HER HOME. TELL HER MOTHER
WHERE WE FOUND HER.
SAM !

01:21:28.151 --> 01:21:31.854
YOU LEAVE HER ALONE !
MOVE IT, BOY !

01:21:31.921 --> 01:21:34.257
[ Car Horns Honking ]

01:21:34.323 --> 01:21:36.592
PLEASE DON'T TELL MY MOTHER.
SHE'S GONNA KILL ME.

01:21:36.659 --> 01:21:39.929
PILAR !
DON'T ARGUE WITH ME.
GIT !

01:21:39.996 --> 01:21:43.566
[ Honking Continues ]

01:21:43.632 --> 01:21:47.036
[ Honking Echoing ]

